<a name="overview"></a><h3>Overview</h3>
<p><br>
This interdepartmental major enables students to concentrate the program of study on a particular subject area which touches several different disciplines. Students may earn either a Bachelor of Arts or a Bachelor of Science degree in Urban Studies. Students should consult with the urban studies coordinator (currently Dr. Peter Tobias) to select courses and to determine the appropriate Senior Seminar as a culmination of their studies. Students also must meet the general education requirements for their degree. 
