<HEAD>
<TITLE>HOW TO ORDER A TRANSCRIPT</TITLE>
<BASE HREF="http://www.rockford.edu/">
</HEAD>

<BODY>
<h1>HOW TO ORDER A TRANSCRIPT</H1>
<h2>We need the following:</h2>
<ul>
<LI> 1) Your full and complete name, including any previous names. 

<LI> 2) Your social security number.

<LI> 3) Your current address and phone number.  (Many times we are unable to locate a transcript because we are not given a maiden name, etc., and we need to call you.)

<LI> 4) Dates of attendance at Rockford College/Regent's College.

<LI> 5) Complete name and mailing address of person or institution to whom you wish your transcript sent.

<LI> 6) Conclude your note requesting the transcript with your signature.  It is a federal law that we must have the student's signature to release a transcript.

<LI> 7) Include either a check or money order, payable to Rockford College, in the amount of $3.00 per transcript ordered.

<LI> 8) Mark the lower left corner of the envelope "TRANSCRIPT REQUEST".
</ul>
<P>Send your request and payment to:</P>
<pre>
     Rockford College
     Office of Registration
     5050 East State Street
     Rockford, IL  61108-2393
</pre>

<P>If you wish to have extra Transcript Request Forms sent to you,
please indicate that in your letter.</P>


