<H2><A NAME="The Program"></A>The Program</H2>

<P>The Lady Regents are rebuilding for a run at the NIIC championship.
Although very young, the team is built around Junior Staci Brown, a 6'-1&quot;
post player. They open with the 18th Regent Classic and also play in the
Lakeland College Tourney in December, before opening conference play in
January.</P>

<H2><A NAME="Mark Capps, Head Coach"></A>Mark Capps, Head Coach</H2>

<P>In his second year at the college level, Coach Capps is adjusting to
the rigors of recruiting and holding a team together in a private school.
Coach Capps was a very successful high school basketball coach in Rochelle,
IL before joining the Regents. He also serves Rockford College as an Admission
Representative.</P>

<P><BR>
</P>

