<P><tbody><rows></P>

<P></ROWS></TBODY></P>
</CAPTION>

<TR>
<TD align="center"><IMG SRC="rcsign3.gif" HEIGHT=142 WIDTH=162></TD>

<TD align="center">
<H1>Women's Volleyball<BR>
Rockford College </H1>
</TD>

<TD><IMG SRC="campus1.gif" HEIGHT=98 WIDTH=261></TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>

<P><BR clear="left">
<A HREF="#The Program">The Program</A></P>

<P><A HREF="#Joan Mosher, Head Coach">The Coach</A></P>

<P><A HREF="#The Schedule">The Schedule</A></P>

<H2><A NAME="The Program"></A>The Program</H2>

<P>Rockford College volleyball program is in the rebuilding stage and the
new coach is looking for talented players with which to rebuild the program.
</P>

<H2><A NAME="Joan Mosher, Head Coach"></A>Joan Mosher, Head Coach</H2>

<P>Joan Mosher is looking forward to revitalizing the volleyball program
at Rockford College. &quot;We have a good core of the team returning for
the 96 season on which to build,&quot; she states. &quot;With a few new
players, we can expect much success this season. I bring with me many years
of volleyball experience, both coaching and playing.&quot; After playing
high school ball at Rockford East, she attended Rockford College for undergraduate
work on a Merit Scholarship (which combined academics and athletics), lettering
in volleyball, basketball, field hockey, and softball. In 1986, Coach Mosher
was honored by being inducted into the college's Athletic Hall of Fame.
&quot;Volleyball has been a love of my life,&quot; she explains. &quot;Not
only did it help in furthering my education on and off the court but it
has turned into a family affair. My sister and I have played together on
teams for almost 20 years. Now my two daughters are carrying on the tradition
by participating in club volleyball in the Great Lakes Region and on their
school teams. Rockford College has also been a huge influence in my life.
It provided me with an excellent education, introduced me to a lot of great
people, including my husband, and left me with great pride in my self and
my school. That pride is what I hope to instill in the players on my team.&quot;
<BR>
<BR>
</P>

<P>&nbsp;</P>

<H2><A NAME="The Schedule"></A>The Schedule</H2>

