<table border="2">
<tbody><rows>    <tr>
        <td align="center"><img src="rcsign3.gif" width="162"
        height="142"></td>
        <td align="center"><h1>Cheerleading<br>
        Rockford College</h1>
        </td>
        <td><img src="campus1.gif" width="261" height="98"></td>
    </tr>
</ROWS></TBODY></table>

<p><br clear="left">
</p>

<h2>The Program</h2>

<p>Cheerleading and poms at Rockford College seems to evolve as
the years go. We have now moved to a coed Cheer squad and a dance line.
These are picked at the Try-outs in the Spring and Fall. </p>

<h2>The Coach</h2>

<p>Gayle Strang, advisor-coach has been at the college 28
years. This year's squad has been led by Mike Smith, a former male-
cheerleader who has been able to help teach lifts and holds. It's 
been exciting to see the changes. <br>
<br>
<br>
</p>

