<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Rockford College - Computer Center</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY>
<H1><CENTER>Rockford College<BR>Computer Center</CENTER></H1>
<HR>
<P>
The Rockford College <STRONG>Computer Center</STRONG> is located on the
lower level of the <A HREF="/images/colman2.gif">Howard Colman Library</A>
Building.  The Computer Center is responsible for both administrative and 
academic computing at Rockford College, including the <A HREF="/images/lab1.gif">
Academic Computing Lab</A>, which is located on the lower level of the
<A HREF="/images/starr2.gif">Starr Science Building</A>.</P>
<P>
Our adminstrative computing system consists of SCT's IA-PLUS SIS, FRS, and 
ADS software running on an <A HREF="/images/4381a.gif">IBM 4381-91E mainframe
system</A>.  We operate both IBM VM and VSE/ESA environments.  Our report
writing is accomplished using IBI's FOCUS report writer.  We also make use
of SAS software and a variety of other utilities, COBOL programs, etc.
</P>
<P>
Our <A HREF="/images/lab2.gif">Student Computer Labs</A> operate on a 
Novell Netware 4.1 network with connections to the Internet provided via
our internet provider, <A HREF="http://www.illinois.net">netILLINOIS</A>.
Our current link is a 56k connection but we hope to upgrade to T-1 in the
near future.  Our campus network utilizes a variety of applications 
including Netscape, Lotus cc:Mail, WordPerfect and Lotus 123.  The student
labs are supervised by the Computer Center but student lab assistants 
perform all daily operations and support.
</P>
<P>
<UL>
Currently, the Computer Center's staff consists of 5 employees:

<LI><A HREF="/images/bill.gif">Bill White, Director</A>
E-Mail: <A HREF="mailto:bwhite@rockford.edu">bwhite@rockford.edu</A>
<LI><A HREF="/images/pattie.gif">Patricia Potter, Technology Support Analyst</A>
E-Mail: <A HREF="mailto:ppotter@rockford.edu">ppotter@rockford.edu</A>


<LI><A HREF="/images/kelly.gif">Kelly Sartorius, Technology Support Analyst</A>
E-Mail: <A HREF="mailto:ksartorius@rockford.edu">ksartorius@rockford.edu</A>
<LI>Kathy Roerkohl, Technology Support Coordinator
E-Mail: <A HREF="mailto:kroerkohl@rockford.edu">kroerkohl@rockford.edu</A>

<LI>Roslynn Roberts, Computer Operator
E-Mail: <A HREF="mailto:rroberts@rockford.edu">rroberts@rockford.edu</A>
</UL>
</P>
<P>
Each member of the Computer Center staff shares in all responsibilities,
including mainframe operations, administrative programming & support, 
network support, and PC hardware & software support.
</P>

<HR>
