<h2>  ROCKFORD COLLEGE ACADEMIC CALENDAR - SPRING 1997</h2>


<h3>January 12</h3>

Residence halls open for new students. (1 p.m.)

<h3>January 13</h3>

Orientation for international students.

<h3>January 14</h3>

Orientation/registration for new students.

<h3>January 15</h3>

Residence halls open for returning students. (10 a.m.)

<h3>January 16</h3>

CLASSES BEGIN. (8 a.m.)

<h3>January 20</h3>

MARTIN LUTHER KING DAY OBSERVED.  NO CLASSES.  Offices open.

<h3>January 31</h3>

Last day to add a course. (4 p.m.)

<h3>February 7</h3>

Last day to drop a course without notation. (4 p.m.)<br>
Last day to file credit/audit forms. (4 p.m.)

<h3>February 17</h3>

Presidents' Day.  Classes in session.  Offices open.

<h3>February 21</h3>

Charter Day Convocation. (4 p.m.)

<h3>February 28</h3>

Last day to file pass/fail forms. (4 p.m.)

<h3>March 3-7</h3>

Mid-term exams.

<h3>March 7</h3>

Mid-term grades due in Registration Office. (4 p.m.)<br>
Residence halls close. (7 p.m.)

<h3>March 8-16</h3>

SPRING BREAK.  NO CLASSES.  Offices Open.

<h3>March 16</h3>

Residence halls open. (1 p.m.)

<h3>March 17</h3>

CLASSES RESUME. (8 a.m.)

<h3>March 27-30</h3>

EASTER RECESS.  NO CLASSES.<br>
<i>(March 28: Offices closed for Easter recess)</i>

<h3>March 31</h3>

CLASSES RESUME. (8 a.m.)<br>
Last day to withdraw with "W". (4 p.m.)

<h3>April 7-18</h3>

Academic advising for fall semester pre-registration.

<h3>April 21</h3>

Registration for Summer Session begins.

<h3>April 21-25</h3>

Pre-registration for fall semester.

<h3>April 30</h3>

Honor's Day Convocation. (4 p.m.)

<h3>May 7</h3>

CLASSES END. (10 p.m.)

<h3>May 8</h3>

Final exams for Thursday evening classes.

<h3>May 9-13</h3>

Final exams.(Wednesday evening final exams on Friday evening)

<h3>May 14</h3>

All final grades due in Registration Office. (9 a.m.)<br>
Conflict exams.  (Grades due 9 a.m. Thursday).<br>
Residence halls close for all except graduates. (4 p.m.)

<h3>May 15</h3>
Commencement rehearsal & Senior Picnic (following rehearsal) (4 p.m.)

<h3>May 16-17</h3>

Alumni reunion.

<h3>May 18</h3>

Baccalaureate. (10 a.m.)<br>
COMMENCEMENT. (11:30 am)

<h3>May 19</h3>

Residence halls close for graduating seniors. (12 p.m.)

<P>Final grades are due 48 hours after each exam, but no later than 9 a.m., Wednesday, May 14, for regular
exams.</P>


