<DOCOLDNO>IA016-000171-B003-437</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.rockford.edu:80/academic/catalog/math/detail.htm 192.217.12.8 19970105235424 text/html 12518
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
