<body background="cr.gif">

<center><font size=8 color="ff0000">Mission Statement:</font></center>

<p><img src="t.gif" border=0 height=20 width=20 align=bottom><font size=4>

<b>he
mission of the Rockford College Republican Club is to provide students,
faculty, and staff a positive forum in which conservative beliefs and views
are not condemned as &quot;not politically correct.&quot;  As part of this
mission, the Republican Club offers its members the ability to network with
other conservatives, participate in conservative events, meet and develop
interpersonal relationships with republican politicians, and participate
in government on the local, state, and national levels.

</b></font></p>

</body>
</html>

