<DOCHDR>
http://www.rockford.edu:80/academic/catalog/compsci/detail.htm 192.217.12.8 19970105235914 text/html 13570
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Sun, 05 Jan 1997 23:42:44 GMT
