<DOCOLDNO>IA016-000171-B005-48</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.rockford.edu:80/academic/catalog/nurse/detail.htm 192.217.12.8 19970106000018 text/html 10971
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
