<DOCNO>WT23-B01-118</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA016-000171-B004-325</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.rockford.edu:80/academic/catalog/biology/detail.htm 192.217.12.8 19970105235836 text/html 15799
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
