<DOCHDR>
http://www.rockford.edu:80/academic/catalog/british/courses.htm 192.217.12.8 19970105234949 text/html 1614
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Sun, 05 Jan 1997 23:33:21 GMT
