<HTML>

<HEAD>
<TITLE>British Studies Minor Requirements</TITLE>
<!-- Keep the below line commented out until loaded to Web Server -->
<!-- <BASE HREF="http://www.rockford.edu/"> -->
</HEAD>

<BODY>

<CENTER>
<H1>Rockford College<BR>
British Studies (Minor)</H1>
</CENTER>
<HR>

<H2>Minor Requirements -- 20 Hours</H2>

<PRE>
<A HREF="/academic/catalog/british/detail.htm#201">Eng 201 Survey of English Literature I 3 hours</A>
<A HREF="/academic/catalog/british/detail.htm#202">Eng 202 Survey of English Literature II 3 hours</A>

Two of the following:

<A HREF="/academic/catalog/british/detail.htm#210">Hist 210 History of England Since the Conquest 4 hours</A>
<A HREF="/academic/catalog/british/detail.htm#300">Hist 300 Civilization of London (Regent's College only) 4 hours</A>
<A HREF="/academic/catalog/british/detail.htm#324">Hist 324 Tudor-Stuart England 4 hours</A>

Elective courses: At least six hours of 200- or 300-level course-work 
which focuses substantially on Britain, chosen with approval of the chair of 
the English Department. 
</PRE>

