portrait Mel Gibson Braveheart William Wallace Robert Bruce glamour makeover 
face history">
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR=#ffffc0>


<A HREF="../au/">
<STRONG>BIRDHOUSES, CERAMIC CATS</STRONG></A> 

<HR><BR
<CENTER><H1>FUN PORTRAITS OF ALL THE FAMILY USING DIGITAL PHOTOGRAPH ENHANCEMENT</H1></CENTER>

<CENTER><H2>EXPLORE THE EXCITING RANGE OF POSSIBILITIES LISTED BELOW</H2></CENTER>
<BR><HR><BR>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="art.html">
<STRONG>ARTAFACE:  Your Face in Art</STRONG></A> puts your face into a famous 
painting.

<LI><A HREF="Prom.html">
<STRONG>Prom Night 2006 </STRONG></A>age progresses your child's photo to show them older.

<LI><A HREF="makeover.html">
<STRONG>Glamorize</STRONG></A> makes a person look like a million dollars.

<LI><A HREF="Hair.html"><STRONG>Hair change</STRONG></A> shows different 
hairstyles on the same person.

<LI><A HREF="ManWoman.html">
<STRONG>Sex change</STRONG></A> shows how you might look after a change of 
gender.

<LI><A HREF="skinny.html"><STRONG>Look skinny</STRONG></A> makes your photo 
thinner.

<LI><A HREF="YourFaceInHistory.html">
<STRONG>Your face in history</STRONG></A> puts your face into a famous 
historical setting.

</UL>

<CENTER>

<CENTER><A HREF="art.html">
<STRONG>ARTAFACE:  Your Face in Art</STRONG><IMG SRC="renfrabutton.gif"></A></CENTER>

<A HREF="Prom.html">
<STRONG>Prom Night 2006 </STRONG><IMG SRC="zoebutton.gif"></A> 
<A HREF="makeover.html">
<STRONG>Glamorize</STRONG><IMG SRC="fhbutton.gif"></A> </CENTER>

<CENTER><A HREF="Hair.html">
<STRONG>Hair change</STRONG><IMG SRC="nic2button.gif"></A>

<A HREF="ManWoman.html">
<STRONG>Sex change</STRONG><IMG SRC="manwbutton.gif"></A>

<A HREF="skinny.html"><STRONG>Look skinny</STRONG><IMG SRC="skinnybutton.gif"></A>
<A HREF="YourFaceInHistory.html">
<STRONG>Your face in history</STRONG><IMG SRC="clydemelbutton.gif"></A></CENTER>
<BR>
<IMG SRC="/Net_Gifs/Bars/GreyCircleBlueBar.gif", ALT="[colorful divider]">
<BR>

<P>Please check out this as well
<A HREF="../Wallace/index.html"><STRONG>Images of Wallace and Bruce</STRONG>
<IMG SRC="ww4button.gif"></A>
<BR>
<IMG SRC="/Net_Gifs/Bars/GreyCircleBlueBar.gif", ALT="[colorful divider]">
<BR>
<BR>

<UL>
<LI>Ever wonder what you would look like in a 
<A HREF="makeover.html">glamour photo shoot?</A></LI>
<LI>Ever wonder how your friend or relative would look after a 
makeover?</LI>
<LI>Do you want to try a radical new hairstyle?</LI>
<LI>Do you want to see how you would look if you were thinner?</LI>
</UL>
</P>
<P>Wonder no more! Our digital photographic enhancement can show you these 
changes without your having to do a thing!  Just send us a 
photograph and tell us what you want done to it.  We will send you back 
your original photo plus a 5" by 7" computer generated image.</P>
<BR>
<P>Please tell us which of the following options you have chosen:</P>
<OL>
<LI><A HREF="Prom.html">age progress</A> your child to 18 years old;</LI> 
<LI><A HREF="makeover.html">glamorize</A> any face without a trip to the beauty shop;</LI>
<LI><A HREF="Hair.html">radical new hairstyle </A> [specify length and color of hair]</LI>
<LI>See yourself in a famous work of<A HREF="art.html"> art</A> </LI>

<LI>Be inspired by <A HREF="skinny.html">a thinner you</A></LI>
<LI>See yourself as a sibling of the <A HREF="ManWoman.html">opposite
</A> gender.</LI>
<LI>See yourself in a <A HREF="YourFaceInHistory.html">famous 
historical</A> context</A></LI>
</OL>
<BR><HR>
<P>
SEND US YOUR REQUEST with a 5" by 7" original (or smaller...bear in 
mind that smaller originals do not produce as sharp a final result) 
and a self-addressed stamped envelope.<BR>
<BR>
Make checks or money orders payable to Magic Dragon.<BR>
Send $19.95 (black and white) or $39.95 (color) to<BR>
<BR> 

<CENTER>
<P>Magic Dragon Multimedia<BR>
Post Office Box 40009<BR>
Pasadena, CA  91114-7009<BR>
</P>
</CENTER>

