**************************************************************</CENTER>

<BR><A HREF="aliens.html"><STRONG>ALIENS</STRONG></A>: list of 31 movies/TV movies with Aliens, last updated 19 July 1996
<BR><A HREF="authors.html"><STRONG>AUTHORS</STRONG></A>: list of 1,502 links, last updated 11 Jan 1997
     also some brief notes on 2,273 authors and pseudonyms NOT on the Internet, last updated 
     9 Jan 1997, for a total of 3,775 authors' hotlinks or names or pseudonyms or notes
<BR><A HREF="books.html"><STRONG>BOOK TITLES</STRONG></A>: and Book reviews, list of 9 links, last updated 31 Dec 1996
<BR><A HREF="countries.html"><STRONG>COUNTRIES</STRONG></A>: Fascinating 
     essays on the authors, magazines, and publishers of specific 
     countries, as well as a distributed debate on which country is the 
     true birthplace of science fiction; is also a list of links to 
     authors and magazines from 35 individual countries, annotated, last updated 
     9 Jan 1997, plus essentially void entries on 32 countries for which 
     the webmaster solicits information from fans.
     New essay added, under the ISRAEL entry: JEWS AND JEWISH SCIENCE FICTION
     Warning: 113 Kilobytes text will load slowly for those with slow 
     modems.
<BR><A HREF="games.html"><STRONG>GAMES/SOFTWARE</STRONG></A>: list of 23 links, last updated 5 Sep 1996
<BR><A HREF="general.html"><STRONG>GENERAL INTEREST</STRONG></A>: SCIENCE FICTION: list of 67 links, last updated 1 Jan 1997
<BR><A HREF="magazines.html"><STRONG>MAGAZINES/NEWSLETTERS</STRONG></A>: list of 83 links, last updated 11 January 1997, 
     plus data on 414 magzines NOT on the Web, last updated 31 Dec 1996
<BR><A HREF="movies.html"><STRONG>MOVIES</STRONG></A>: list of lists, 20 links, last updated 2 January 1997
<BR><A HREF="pub.html"><STRONG>PUBLISHERS & BOOKSTORES</STRONG></A>: list of 30 bookstores/publishers, last updated 24 Dec 1996
<BR><A HREF="stories.html"><STRONG>STORIES AND/OR HYPERTEXT TITLES</STRONG></A>: list of 7 links, last updated 31 Dec 1996
<BR><A HREF="tv.html"><STRONG>TELEVISION</STRONG></A>: list of 99 links, 276 shows, last updated 4 January 1997
     New: many little-known golden-age shows, annotations/essays, and many cast lists added recently.
     Several more British series and several more TV movies added.  Director and 
     Producer and Story Editor credits updated.
     Warning: 167 Kilobytes text will load slowly for those with slow 
     modems.  In a few weeks I'll break this into a tree of small, 
     fast-loading files.
<BR><A HREF="time.html"><STRONG>TIME TRAVEL</STRONG></A>: List of 65 movies about time travel, last updated 19 July 1996
