on the Web relating to Science Fiction Cinema, CINESCAPE Magazine, Jan/Feb 
1997, "They Surf By Night", story by Assistant Editor Kristin Kloberdanz, 
p.75.  For subscription information on CINESCAPE, write to 434 W. Downer 
Place, Aurora IL 60506, or telephone (630) 892-7465 between 9 a.m. and 5 
