<H1>Malibu Real Estate</H1>
<H2>Acreage with Commanding Views, Scenic Beauty and Security</H2>
<HR SIZE="5">
<H5>Please refer to this site for updates. Don't forget that you can click on pictures with a highlighted edge to view a larger image. This site is best viewed with Netscape 2.0 or newer.</H5></CENTER>
<HR SIZE="5">
<IMG SRC="neighbors.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER="3">
<H3>There is no better deal for. . . </H3><H2>LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION</H2>

<H4>. . .your home will have the most incredible views of the blue Pacific Ocean including breathtaking sunsets and sunrises, the sparkling city lights at night of Los Angeles.  Your home is a 5 mile drive to the beaches and 
<A HRef="http://www.west.net/~gomalibu/index.shtml">city of Malibu</A>,
a 15 mile drive through the scenic <A HRef="http://www.nps.gov/samo/">Santa Monica Mountains</A> to the bustling <A HRef="http://www.sfvalley.org/">San Fernando Valley</A> or a 17 mile drive into the big city of <A HRef="http://www.smweb.com/calendar.htm">Santa Monica</A> and <A HRef="http://www.insidewla.com/quick.htm">West Los Angeles</A>. You will have privacy and security. Nearby perks include horse trails, <A HRef="http://www.nps.gov/samo/">hiking</A>, <A HRef="http://www.geocities.com/Paris/4198/hrfwww.htm">sailing</A>, <A HRef="http://ladining.com/cgi/ladining.pl?Location=Beaches">fine dining</A> and <A HRef="http://www.worldgolf.com/courses/unitedstates/california/califg10.html">golf</A>.</H4>
<BR>
<HR SIZE="5">
