<BODY>

<CENTER><H1>I'M CERTIFIED FOR SLEEP</H1></CENTER><P>
<BR> 
 
<CENTER>
<H3>by</H3>
</CENTER>
<BR><CENTER>
<H3>Jonathan Vos Post</H3>
</CENTER>
<CENTER>
<H3>Christine Carmichael</H3>
</CENTER>
<CENTER>
<H3>Andrew Post</H3>
</CENTER>

<CENTER>
<H3><I>Illustrated  by  Katherine  O'Brien</I></H3>
</CENTER>


<HR>
<BR>

<CENTER>
<TABLE BORDER=5><TR><TD>
<IMG 
SRC="sleep1.gif"></TD></TR></TABLE>
<CAPTION>
<H4>Pyjama Police!  Up and at 'em</H4>
</CAPTION></CENTER>
<BR>

<CENTER>
<P>Imagine a world where you need a license to sleep<BR>
</CENTER>
<CENTER>
<P>If you don't have one, the Pyjama Police<BR>
</CENTER>
<CENTER>
<P>poke you with batons when you doze off<BR>
</CENTER>
<BR><BR>
<CENTER>
<TABLE BORDER=5><TR><TD>
<IMG 
SRC="sleep2.gif"></TD></TR></TABLE>
<CAPTION>
<H4>Here ya go, sweetie, one sleep permit.  Have a nice nap.</H4>
</CAPTION></CENTER>
<BR>
<CENTER>
<P>Up to age 16, you only need a learner's permit<BR>
</CENTER>
<CENTER>
<P>for sleepwalking and daydreaming<BR>
</CENTER>
<BR><BR>
<CENTER>
