                               server allotments">
<BODY BGCOLOR=#FFFFc0>
<P>
<CENTER>
<H2>Magic Dragon Multimedia<BR>
Internet Rental Rates:</H2>
</CENTER>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/Net_Gifs/Bars/HLINE.GIF", ALT="[Product photo thumbnail]">
</P>

</P>
<TABLE BORDER>
<CAPTION ALIGN="TOP">
<H2>Price List</H2>
</CAPTION>
<TR ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN=BASELINE>
<TH>Memory Size</TH>
<TH>Up-Front Cost</TH>
</TR>

<TR ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN=TOP>
<TH><H3>2 megabyte</H3></TH>
<TD>$1000</TD>
</TR>

<TR ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN=TOP>
<TH><H3>1 megabyte</H3></TH>
<TD>$750</TD>
</TR>

<TR ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN=TOP>
<TH><H3>500 kByte</H3></TH>
<TD>$500</TD>
</TR>

<TR ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN=TOP>
<TH><H3>100 kByte</H3></TH>
<TD>$250</TD>
</TR>

</TABLE>
<P>
<STRONG>You can have large amounts of text, plus pictures on your website.  For 
example:</STRONG><P>
<UL>
<LI>a 100k site could easily support 25 to 30 pages of text plus 1 or 2 
pictures</LI>
<LI>a 500k site could hold hundreds of pages of text plust 2 or 3 simple 
pictures</LI>
<LI>a 1 megabyte site could hold any novel plus several pictures</LI>
<LI>a 2 megabyte site could hold 10 to 15 pictures plus copious text</LI>
<LI>the more detailed the pictures, the fewer that can be supported</LI>
</UL><P>

<STRONG>Home Page Development</STRONG>
<OL>
<LI>You supply the copy, illustrations, and vision of your enterprise.</LI>
<LI>We do the <STRONG>scanning</STRONG>, if necessary. </LI>
<LI>We supply tools for <STRONG>graphics</STRONG> and <STRONG>copy editing</STRONG>.</LI>
<LI>We generate the <STRONG>HTML</STRONG> (HyperText Markup Language) to 
implement your project at a rate of $40/hour, one hour minimum.</LI>
<LI>We provide <STRONG>online preview</STRONG> if you don't have internet 
yourself.</LI>
</OL>
<P>
<LI>free <STRONG>updates</STRONG> the first year</LI>
<P><LI><STRONG>hot-links</STRONG> for customers to e-mail the home 
page owner (probably you)</LI>
<P><LI><STRONG>hot-links</STRONG> to other websites (get permission first!) 
</OL>
