<CENTER><H2>Your Face in History</H2></CENTER><P>
<HR><BR>

<P>This makes a fun gift for somebody you know, yourself included.  See 
your face on the shoulders of a famous hero, send your old school friends copies of 
you apparently chatting to some famous filmstar, amaze your family with 
pictures of you being congratulated by dead presidents (shades of Forrest 
Gump!)  All you need to do is send us copies of the two photos or pictures you 
want us to put together plus a money order ($19.95 black and white, $39.95 
color) plus a stamped self-addressed photograph envelope.<BR><BR>


