<TITLE>Prom Night 2006</TITLE>
<META NAME="Author" CONTENT="Christine Carmichael">
<META NAME="Keywords" CONTENT="photo enhancement prom night hairstyles age 
                           progression digital sex change skinny snapshots 
                           glamour makeover face in history">
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="artBG.gif">

<CENTER><H2>Prom Night 2006</H2></CENTER>

<IMG SRC="/Net_Gifs/Bars/GreyLinedBar.gif", ALT="[Horizontal Line]">
<BR><HR><BR>
<CENTER>
|<A HREF="commercial.html">RATES</A>
|<A HREF="../noframe.html">Magic Dragon Multimedia</A>
 |<A HREF="../PhotoEnhancement/index.html">PHOTO/GIFTS</A>
 |<A HREF="../Wallace/index.html">Wallace</A>
 |<A HREF="../Wallace/mel.html">Mel Gibson</A>
 |<A HREF="UltimateSF/SF-Index.html" TARGET="_blank">SF</A>
 |<A HREF="../EmeraldCity/index.html" TARGET="_blank">WRITINGS</A>
 |<A HREF="UltimateMystery/Mystery-Index.html" TARGET="_blank"> MYSTERY</A> 
 |<A HREF="../ComputerFutures/index.html">COMPFUT</A> 
 |<A HREF="/HaversineEnterprises/framed.html">HAVERSINE</A> 
 |<A HREF="PersonalEnglish/index.html">PEC</A>|
 |<A HREF="/SherlockHolmes/index.html">HOLMES</A>|
</CENTER>
<BR><HR><BR>

<P>
Ever wonder what your child will look like on prom night?  Wonder no 
more!  We can age progress a photograph of your child to show how he/she 
might look when grown up.  
</P>
<HR><BR>

<CENTER>
<TABLE BORDER=5><TR><TD><A HREF="ru18.gif">
<IMG SRC="ru18Small.gif",ALT="[Product photo thumbnail]"></TD></TR>
</TABLE><CAPTION>click here to enlarge</CAPTION>
</CENTER><HR><BR>
<P>Look at the examples shown above: a six-year-old boy 
and an eight-year-old girl have been age progressed to eighteen by a digital
process.  If you look carefully, you can see the original features are 
basically the same, but the result shows a more mature face.
<P>Here are some more examples:
<CENTER>
<TABLE BORDER=5><TR><TD>  
  <A HREF="ru18black.gif"><IMG SRC="ru18blackSmall.gif",
    ALT="[Product photo thumbnail]"></TD></TR>
</TABLE><CAPTION>click here to enlarge</CAPTION>
</CENTER>
<HR><BR>
<CENTER><TABLE BORDER=5><TR><TD>  
  <A HREF="after.html"><IMG SRC="afterbutton.gif",
    ALT="[Product photo thumbnail]"></TD></TR>
</TABLE><CAPTION>click here to see some more before and after pictures</CAPTION>
</CENTER>
<HR><BR>
<P> While we cannot guarantee that your child's facial structure will  develop in exactly the same way as our image suggests, we think that you  will be pleased with the results.  If you are truly dissatisfied with  the result, <STRONG>we will refund your money.</STRONG>
<BR><HR>
<P>Most of these examples were produced from ordinary school photographs.
Send us a 5" by 7" photo of your child (or smaller...bear in 
mind that smaller originals do not produce as sharp a final result), 
and a self-addressed stamped envelope.<BR>
<BR>
Make checks or money orders payable to Magic Dragon Multimedia.<BR>
Send $19.95 (black and white) or $39.95 (color) to<BR>
<BR> 

<CENTER>
<P>Magic Dragon Multimedia<BR>
Post Office Box 40009<BR>
Pasadena, CA  91114-7009<BR>
</P>
</CENTER>


