<HEAD>
<TITLE>Photo Enhancement: Makeover</TITLE>
<META NAME="Author" CONTENT="Christine Carmichael">
<META NAME="Keywords" CONTENT="photo enhancement prom night hairstyles age 
                           progression skinny snapshots 
                           glamour makeover">
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR=#ffffc0>

<CENTER><H2>Makeover Possibitilties: an easy tryout</H2></CENTER>
<HR>
<H2><CENTER>What?  Me glamorous?</CENTER></H2>

<UL>
<LI>Ever wonder what you would look like in a 
glamour photo shoot?</LI>
<LI>Ever wonder how your friend or relative would look after a 
makeover?</LI>
<H2>Before and After</H2>

<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="framedcmc.gif", ALT="Makeover Illustration 1"> </CENTER>
<P>
Using the fuzzy and definitely unglamorous starting point shown in the 
Before photo, the digital process will given her a much more sophisticated 
look. 
<H3>Click on the glamorize button to see what we have done with this image</H3>
<CENTER><A HREF="hairup.html"><IMG SRC="glambutton.gif"></A></CENTER>

<BR>
<HR>
<P>Here is another example:
<CENTER>
<H2>Before</H2><IMG SRC="ccbefore.gif">    <A HREF="glam.html">
 <IMG SRC="glambutton.gif"></A>
</CENTER>

<BR>
<HR>
<P> Our digital photographic enhancement can show you these 
changes to your hair, face or body without your having to do a thing!  Just send us a 
photograph and tell us what you want done to it.  We will send you back 
your original photo plus a 5" by 7" computer generated image.</P>
<BR>
<P>Please tell us which of the following options you have chosen:</P>
<OL>

<LI><A HREF="makeover.html">glamorize</A> any face without a trip to the beauty shop;</LI>
<LI><A HREF="Hair.html">radical new hairstyle </A>
[specify length and color of hair]</LI>
<LI><A HREF="skinny.html">a thinner you</A></LI>
</OL>
<BR>
<P>
Include a 5" by 7" original (or smaller...bear in 
mind that smaller originals do not produce as sharp a final result) 
and a self-addressed stamped envelope.<BR>
<BR>
Make checks or money orders payable to Magic Dragon.<BR>
Send $19.95 (black and white) or $39.95 (color) to<BR>
<BR> 

<CENTER>
<P>Magic Dragon Multimedia<BR>
Post Office Box 40009<BR>
Pasadena, CA  91114-7009<BR>
</P>
</CENTER>


