limited to <STRONG>173</STRONG> shows broadcast in the United States (wherever originated),
and <STRONG>195</STRONG> shows listed with no hotlinks currently known to this compiler
for a total of <STRONG>275</STRONG> television shows and/or hotlinks

Updated 11 January 1997

Warning: this is 169 kilobytes of text, and it will be a few weeks before 
I break it down into a tree of faster-loading little files.  It will load 
slowly for those with slow modems, and not in its entirety for those with 
very small memories.

Copyright 1996,1997 by Magic Dragon Multimedia.<BR>
All rights reserved.  May not be reproduced without permission.  <BR>
