The Ray Bradbury Theatre, HBO and USA, 1985-1987
    Filmed in Canada and New Zealand to save money, immortal writer ray 
    Bradbury showed a strong hand as producer of sometimes stunning, 
    sometimes poignant, sometimes nostalgic, occasionally surprising 
    dramatizations of some of the finest short stories to ever be screened
