<A HREF="http://us.imdb.com/M/title-exact?Philadelphia%20Experiment,%20The%20(1984)">Philadelphia Experiment, The (1984)</A>
<A HREF="http://us.imdb.com/M/title-exact?Playing%20Beatie%20Bow%20(1986)">Playing Beatie Bow (1986)</A>
<A HREF="http://us.imdb.com/M/title-exact?Quantum%20Leap%20(1989)(TV)">Quantum Leap (1989) (TV)</A>
<A HREF="http://us.imdb.com/M/title-exact?Roman%20Scandals%20(1933)">Roman Scandals (1933)</A>
<A HREF="http://us.imdb.com/M/title-exact?Running%20Against%20Time%20(1990)(TV)">Running Against Time (1990)(TV)</A>
<A HREF="http://us.imdb.com/M/title-exact?Star%20Trek%20IV:%20The%20Voyage Home%20(1986)">Star Trek IV: The Voyage Home (1986)</A>
<A HREF="http://us.imdb.com/M/title-exact?Star%20Trek:%20First%20Contact%20(1996)">Star Trek: First Contact (1996)</A>
<A HREF="http://us.imdb.com/M/title-exact?Star%20Trek:%20Generations%20(1994)">Star Trek: Generations (1994)</A>
<A HREF="http://us.imdb.com/M/title-exact?Terminator%202:%203-D%20(1996)">Terminator 2: 3-D (1996)</A>
<A HREF="http://us.imdb.com/M/title-exact?Terminator,%20The%20(1984)">Terminator, The (1984)</A>
<A HREF="http://us.imdb.com/M/title-exact?Three%20Stooges%20Meet%20Hercules,%20The%20(1962)">Three Stooges Meet Hercules, The (1962)</A>
<A HREF="http://us.imdb.com/M/title-exact?Time%20After%20Time%20(1979)">Time After Time (1979)</A>
<A HREF="http://us.imdb.com/M/title-exact?Time%20Bandits%20(1980)">Time Bandits (1980)</A>
<A HREF="http://us.imdb.com/M/title-exact?Time%20Machine,%20The%20(1960)">Time Machine, The (1960)</A>
<A HREF="http://us.imdb.com/M/title-exact?Time%20Runner%20(1993)">Time Runner (1993)</A>
<A HREF="http://us.imdb.com/M/title-exact?Timecop%20(1994)">Timecop (1994)</A>
<A HREF="http://us.imdb.com/M/title-exact?Timerider%20(1983)">Timerider (1983)</A>
