<STRONG><H2>COUNTRIES</H2></STRONG></A>

<STRONG>UNDER CONSTRUCTION</STRONG>: essays and list of links to 
     authors and magazines from 35 countries, as well as 32 entries which are 
     essentially void about countries with which I have little knowledge,
     for a total of 67 countries
     last updated 11 January 1997
     
     Over 113 kilobytes of text; may load slowly if you have a slow modem.
     
