<A NAME="COUNTRIES-SOUTH-AFRICA"><STRONG><H3>SOUTH AFRICA</H3></STRONG></A>
South Africa, the only country to have the atomic bomb and then renounce 
and abandon it, has a nmber of internationally-published science fiction 
authors, including:
     E. J. Blow
     H. A. Fagan
     W. Rose
     C. C. Reed

