<TITLE>Poetry</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<CENTER><H2>Poetry for reading by Jonathan Vos Post</H2></CENTER>

<OL>
<LI><A HREF="DNA.html">The Twilight of Genetic Engineering</A></LI>
