<H1><CENTER>Current Events Quiz</CENTER>
</H1>
<H3>Choose the best of the given answers:</H3>
<BR><P>
1. Which flight crashed recently near New York City?
<BR><P>
	<INPUT TYPE="radio" VALUE="Mary" NAME="flight">Eastern  737<BR>
	<INPUT TYPE="radio" VALUE="800" NAME="flight">TWA 800<BR>
	<INPUT TYPE="radio" VALUE="Spiro" NAME="flight">Alaska 4321<BR>
	<INPUT TYPE="radio" VALUE="Margot" NAME="flight">SouthWest 39<BR>
	<INPUT TYPE="radio" VALUE="Jacques" NAME="flight">Delta 68<BR>
<BR><P>
2. Atlanta is in the state of  <BR><P>
	<INPUT TYPE="radio" VALUE="Georgia" NAME="Atlanta">Georgia<BR>
	<INPUT TYPE="radio" VALUE="radio" NAME="Atlanta">Florida<BR>
	<INPUT TYPE="radio" VALUE="radio" NAME="Atlanta">South Carolina<BR>
	<INPUT TYPE="radio" VALUE="radio" NAME="Atlanta">Alabama<BR>
	<INPUT TYPE="radio" VALUE="radio" NAME="Atlanta">California<BR>
