	<INPUT TYPE="radio" VALUE="Fulton" NAME="CAGov">Fulton<BR>
	<INPUT TYPE="radio" VALUE="radio" NAME="CAGov">controlled by Sacramento<BR><P>

4. The Russian spacestation is called Mir.  Mir means:<BR><P>
	<INPUT TYPE="radio" VALUE="radio" NAME="Comet">small<BR>
	<INPUT TYPE="radio" VALUE="Mir" NAME="Comet">universe<BR>
	<INPUT TYPE="radio" VALUE="radio" NAME="Comet">bog<BR>
	<INPUT TYPE="radio" VALUE="radio" NAME="Comet">log cabin<BR>
	<INPUT TYPE="radio" VALUE="radio" NAME="Comet">toilet<BR><P>

5. The capital of Russia is<BR><P>
	<INPUT TYPE="radio" VALUE="Pete Wilson" NAME="Korea">Los Angeles<BR>
