	<INPUT TYPE="radio" VALUE="radio" NAME="Nolte">fathered Madonna's child<BR>
	<INPUT TYPE="radio" VALUE="radio" NAME="Nolte">bought Jackie's saddle<BR>
	<INPUT TYPE="radio" VALUE="tuck" NAME="Nolte">had a testicle tuck<BR>
	<INPUT TYPE="radio" VALUE="radio" NAME="Nolte">joined the hat squad<BR>
	<INPUT TYPE="radio" VALUE="radio" NAME="Nolte">married Margot Kidder<BR><P>
	
9. Yassir Arafat has just agreed to<BR><P>
	<INPUT TYPE="radio" VALUE="radio" NAME="Arafat">host the Miss Universe 
	contest<BR>
	<INPUT TYPE="radio" VALUE="Israel" NAME="Arafat">allow Israel to exist<BR>
	<INPUT TYPE="radio" VALUE="radio" NAME="Arafat">conduct the Electric Light 
	Orchestra<BR>
