<HTML><HEAD>
<TITLE>Clyde's Census</TITLE>
</HEAD><BODY>
<H1>Clyde's Survey</H1>
<P>Welcome to  Clyde's Survey.  Please fill out the following
form to the best of your abilities.</P>
<P>Use <STRONG>Submit</STRONG> To submit your results.
<HR>
<FORM METHOD="POST" ACTION="http://www.magicdragon.com/cgi/form1.pl">
<P><STRONG>Name: </STRONG><INPUT TYPE="TEXT" NAME="theName"></P>
