<DOCHDR>
http://www.magicdragon.com:80/HaversineEnterprises/snark.html 206.149.251.176 19970112050255 text/html 6573
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Sun, 12 Jan 1997 05:07:37 GMT
