<LI><A NAME="Perfect Pronunciation on Video"><STRONG>Perfect Pronunciation on 
Video</STRONG></A></LI><A HREF="index.html#Pronunciation">  Main Catalog</A>

<P>The Personal English Company's complete course on pronouncing the 42 sounds
 of Standard American English.  The 16 vowel and diphthong sounds, the 25  
 consonant sounds and 225 NEW practice sentences are demonstrated by
  Charlotte Blackmon on three (3)  1-hr. video tapes.  A new manual completes 
  this handsome boxed set.<STRONG>$100.00</STRONG>
</P>

<HR>

<LI><A NAME="Perfect Pronunciation on Audio">
<STRONG>Perfect Pronunciation on Audio</STRONG></A></LI>
<A HREF="index.html#Pronunciation">Main Catalog</A>
<P>All NEW words and sentences for practice of the 42 sounds of  Standard 
 American English on 2 audio tapes.  Also includes practice exercises on vowel
  contrasts, consonant clusters, pronouncing -s as a word ending, stressed 
  syllable of words, and American intonation. A complete new manual is included
   with the boxed set. <STRONG>$20.00</STRONG></P>
   
<P><A HREF="PerfPron.html">Sample of Content</A></P>
   
