<STRONG>Regular Verbs Used in Business in Present and Past Tenses</STRONG></A>
</LI><A HREF="index.html#Pronunciation">Main Catalog</A>

<P>The pronunciation of -ed, the ending of past tense regular verbs is given 
in the four different ways it is pronounced.  150 of the most frequently used 
verbs in Business are demonstrated on this 2-tape boxed set.  A manual is also 
provided. <STRONG>$20.00</STRONG></P>

<LI><A NAME="Irregular Verbs in Present and Past Tenses">
<STRONG>Irregular Verbs in Present and Past Tenses</STRONG></A>
</LI><A HREF="index.html#Pronunciation">Main Catalog</A>

<P>Eighty percent of communication is in the past tense, and the most commonly
 used verbs are irregular.  This 2-tape set contains pronunciation of the present
  and past tenses of irregular verbs.  A manual is included with the boxed set. 
  <STRONG>$20.00</STRONG></P>
</OL>

