<H3> Meditations Series </H3>
<OL>
<LI><A NAME="On Communicating with Confidence"><STRONG>On Communicating with 
Confidence</STRONG></A><A HREF="index.html#Meditations">Main Catalog</A>

<P>One audio tape contains ideas and suggestions for building greater confidence
 when speaking as a person who speaks English as a second language.  English on
 this tape is at an intermediate level. <STRONG>$20.00</STRONG></P></LI>

<LI><A NAME="On Cultural Differences"><STRONG>On Cultural Differences 
</STRONG></A><A HREF="index.html#Meditations">Main Catalog</A>

<P>One audio tape contains specific information about how the meanings of 
behavior differ from culture to culture.  Some of the topics discussed are 
 how body language, eye contact, and use of physical space differ in showing
 respect in various cultures.  English on this tape is at an intermediate level.
 <STRONG>$20.00</STRONG></P></LI>

<LI><A NAME="American Behavior and Its Meanings in the Office"><STRONG>American
 Behavior and Its Meanings in the Office</STRONG></A>
 <A HREF="index.html#Meditations">Main Catalog</A>

<P>One audio tape contains information on the meanings of the behavior of 
American native speakers of English in the office or business environment; 
how to promote harmony and  cooperative relationships.  English on this tape
is at an intermediate level. <STRONG>$20.00</STRONG></P></LI>

