<CENTER>
<TITLE>Directions to the Site</TITLE></CENTER>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#db9370">
<H2>Directions to the Site of Malibu Estates</H2>
<P>
Your potential home site is located on the <B>ocean side</B> of Saddle Peak at the summit of Piuma Road, west of Las Flores Canyon Road and south of Saddle Peak Road north of Malibu Beach, California.
<P>
If you are <B>traveling west on the Ventura Freeway</B> (Interstate 101) exit and go left on Las Virgenes Road. If you are <B>traveling east on the Ventura Freeway</B> (Interstate 101) exit and go right on Las Virgenes Road. 
<P>
Then turn left on Piuma Road. Piuma Road is past Mulholland Highway. On Piuma road travel to summit. As you begin to go over the hill (views of ocean begin) start looking for the marker on the right side of the road.
<P>  
If you are <B>traveling north on the Pacific Coast Highway</B>, turn right on Las Flores Canyon Road. Las Flores Canyon Road is south of Malibu Canyon Road. When you reach the fork of Schueren Road and Piuma Road, take the left fork onto Piuma Road. On Piuma road travel up to summit. As you approach the summit, start looking for a marker on the left side of the road.
<P>
If you are <B>traveling south on the Pacific Coast Highway</B>, turn left on Las Flores Canyon Road. Las Flores Canyon Road is south of Malibu Canyon Road. When you reach the fork of Schueren Road and Piuma Road, take the left fork onto Piuma Road. On Piuma road travel up to summit. As you approach the summit, start looking for a marker on the left side of the road.
<P><H5>Please refer to this site for direction updates. We will soon provide odometer mileages between points. Don't hesitate to call for directions!</H5> 
<P>
<BR>
<P>
<H3>Contact us for directions: </H3><P>
Linda and Robin Stone at Tel (310)589-9506, Fax (310)589-9306, e-mail venturetech@earthlink.net or write to Malibu Estates, 23852 Pacific Coast Hwy, Suite 740, Malibu, CA 90265 USA.  Please refer to this site for continuous updates. We look forward to hearing from you!! 
