<HEAD>
<TITLE>Faith Fluctuates, July 14, 1996</TITLE>
<META NAME="Author" CONTENT="Rich La Shure">
<META NAME="Keywords" CONTENT="Faith Salvation religion 
                               Theology denominations sacraments
                               Christianity Methodist ">
<META NAME="expiration" CONTENT="December 31, 1996">
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<P>
<A HREF="/SMUMC/index.html"><H2>Return to Sierra Madre UMC home page.</H2></A>

<PRE>
FAITH FLUCTUATES	SERMON BY REV. RICH LA SHURE
ROMANS 7.15-25	JULY 14, 1996

	ONE OF THE GREATEST CHALLENGES FACING THE CHURCHES TODAY IS THE 
CHALLENGE OF DISUNITY. AT LAST COUNT THERE WERE OVER 150 SEPARATE, 
DISTINCT DIVISIONS OR DENOMINATIONS WITHIN THE OVERALL WORLD-WIDE 
CHRISTIAN MOVEMENT, TO SAY NOTHING OF THE LITERALLY THOUSANDS OF 
INDEPENDENT FELLOWSHIPS WHICH HAVE NO DENOMINATIONAL TIE WHATSOEVER. 
WHAT IS A DENOMINATION? A DENOMINATION IS A CORPORATE ENTITY POSSESSING 
ITS OWN UNIQUE RULES AND PROCEDURES FOR THE QUALIFICATION AND ORDINATION 
OF PASTORS, THE MANAGEMENT OF RESOURCES AND THE CARE OF 
CONGREGATIONS. THEOLOGICALLY EACH DIFFERENT DENOMINATION LOOKS AT 
SACRAMENTS DIFFERENTLY; FOR EXAMPLE, THE ROMAN CATHOLIC DENOMINATION 
TEACHES THAT THERE ARE 7 SACRAMENTS WHILE THE UNITED METHODIST 
DENOMINATION TEACHES THAT THERE ARE ONLY 2 SACRAMENTS--BAPTISM AND HOLY 
COMMUNION.
	NOW WHILE THEY ARE SURELY AN IMPORTANT ASPECT OF THE DAY-TO-DAY 
MINISTRIES OF THE CHURCH OF JESUS CHRIST TODAY, DENOMINATIONS ARE NOT 
PART OF THE BIBLICAL PLAN OF GOD FOR THE HUMAN RACE. NO DENOMINATION IS 
EVER MENTIONED ANYWHERE IN THE BIBLE. DENOMINATIONS ARISE OUT OF THE 
DIFFERENCES BETWEEN PEOPLE, USUALLY INVOLVING DISPUTES OVER ONE OF THE 
THREE TS: THEOLOGY, TERRITORY, OR TARGET AUDIENCE.  WHILE UNTOLD MILLIONS 
OF PERSON-HOURS AND PERSON-DOLLARS ARE EXPENDED ANNUALLY TO MAINTAIN 
DENOMINATIONAL STRUCTURES, THESE STRUCTURES ARE OF MEN, NOT OF GOD. 
AMEN?  WHEN WE GET TO HEAVEN, THERE WILL BE NO MORE USE FOR THEM. AMEN? 
	NOW LETS TRY OUT A LITTLE LOGIC HERE, IN THE FORM OF THREE CONNECTED 
PROPOSITIONS:
	PROP. A. JUST TO REPEAT, THERE WONT BE ANY DENOMINATIONS IN HEAVEN. 
HEAVEN WONT RESPECT METHODISTS OVER BAPTISTS OR DISCIPLES OVER 
EVANGELICALS OR PENTECOSTALS OVER CHARISMATICS OR PRE-TRIBULATIONISTS 
OVER PLURALISTS OR CATHOLICS OVER JEHOVAHS WITNESSES.
	PROP. B. A KEY BELIEF AMONG CHRISTIANS IS THAT THE KINGDOMS OF THIS 
WORLD NEED TO BE TRANSFORMED IN THE LIKENESS OF THE KINGDOM OF HEAVEN. 
THAT IS WHY WHEN WE SAY THE LORDS PRAYER WE PRAY, THY KINGDOM COME, THY 
WILL BE DONE ON EARTH AS IT IS IN HEAVEN.
	C.  NOW IF PROPOSITION A AND PROPOSITION B ARE TRUE, THEN IT FOLLOWS 
THAT TO THE DEGREE THAT THEY ARE TRUE FOR US, CHRISTIANS OUGHT TO BE 
WORKING TO OVERCOME THEIR DENOMINATIONAL DIFFERENCES NOW AND NOT 
WAITING FOR GOD TO DO IT IN HEAVEN LATER.    
	OVER MY QUARTER-CENTURY AS A PREACHER, I HAVE HAD SEVERAL 
EXPERIENCES OF UNITY AMONG THE VARIOUS DENOMINATIONS OF THE CHURCH. 
BACK WHEN I WAS A SEMINARY STUDENT, THE RIVERSIDE PRESBYTERY OF THE 
UNITED PRESBYTERIAN CHURCH GRACIOUSLY ALLOWED ME, A UNITED METHODIST, 
TO BE THE PASTOR OF ONE OF ITS SMALLER OUTPOSTS: THE CHARMING SPIRED 
WHITEWASHED WOODEN CHURCH NEAR THE SHORE OF LAKE ELSINORE. THAT WAS A 
WONDERFUL MINISTRY; FOR NEARLY THREE YEARS WE SHARED THE LOVE OF GOD 
TOGETHER ACROSS DENOMINATIONAL LINES.
	THE UNITED METHODIST CHURCH, ALONG WITH SEVERAL OTHER MAINLINE 
DENOMINATIONS INCLUDING THE PRESBYTERIANS AND THE DISCIPLES OF CHRIST, IS 
PART OF COCU, AN ACRONYM WHICH STANDS FOR THE CHURCH OF CHRIST UNITING. 
COCU IS A PRODUCT OF THE LATE 1960S, AND IT HAS ENDURED AS A MOVEMENT 
WITHIN THE MORE LIBERAL WINGS OF THE CHURCH. FROM TIME TO TIME COCU 
DENOMINATIONS DO THINGS TOGETHER TO DEMONSTRATE THEIR UNITY, SUCH AS 
HOLDING JOINT COMMUNION SERVICES OR ORDINATION CEREMONIES. BUT COCU HAS 
NOT ATTRACTED THE INTEREST OF THE MORE CONSERVATIVE DENOMINATIONS LIKE 
THE BAPTISTS. IN FACT, IF YOU MERGED ALL OF THE COCU DENOMINATIONS 
TOGETHER, YOU WOULD GET A DENOMINATION THAT WOULD STILL PLAY SECOND 
FIDDLE TO THE BAPTISTS.
	ANOTHER WAY IN WHICH I HAVE EXPERIENCED UNITY WITHIN THE BODY OF 
CHRIST HAS BEEN THROUGH MINISTERIAL FELLOWSHIPS. THE PROBLEM WITH MANY 
MINISTERIAL FELLOWSHIPS IS THE TENDENCY OF PASTORS TO SPILL THEIR GRIPES 
ABOUT THEIR JOBS, AND THAT DOES NOT TEND TO BE A VERY SPIRITUAL PROCESS. 
HERE IN SIERRA MADRE PASTOR DICK ANDERSON OF THE BIG CONGREGATIONAL 
CHURCH HAS MINISTERED AS A PASTOR TO THE REST OF THE PASTORS, AND HE HAS 
TRULY BLESSED ME IN MY MINISTRY. I ALSO THINK THE WORLD OF PASTOR BARNEY 
HAMADY OF BETHANY CHURCH AND FATHER MICHAEL BAMBERGER OF THE 
EPISCOPAL CHURCH. 
	I AM THINKING BACK TO ONE PARTICULAR TUESDAY AFTERNOON WHEN A 
NUMBER OF US SIERRA MADRE PASTORS MET UP AT THE PASSIONIST FATHERS 
RETREAT CENTER AT THE END OF SUNNYSIDE. WE SAT OUT ON THE VERANDA OF THE 
BUILDING AND GAZED OUT OVER ALL THAT GOD HAS MADE HERE--THE MOUNTAINS, 
THE VALLEY, THE BLUE SKY, TRULY THE GLORY OF CREATION. WE SHARED OUR 
SENSE OF BLESSING AT BEING CALLED TO WORK FOR GOD HERE IN THIS BEAUTIFUL 
PLACE. THAT DAY WE GOT TO MEET SISTER JUDY, WHO CONDUCTS RECOVERY 
RETREATS, DOES GROUP COUNSELING IN OTHER FORMS, AND ORGANIZED THE TAIZE 
SERVICE THAT WAS CONDUCTED DURING ADVENT LAST YEAR. THAT DAY SISTER JUDY 
USED AN EXPRESSION THAT I HAD NEVER HEARD BEFORE: DRY DRUNK.
	AT FIRST, I THOUGHT I HAD LEARNED ANOTHER NEW OXYMORON, LIKE 
NUCLEAR SAFETY, JUMBO SHRIMP, PRETTY UGLY OR VIRTUAL REALITY. AN 
OXYMORON IS A COMPACT CONTRADICTION IN TERMS, A COLLISION BETWEEN 
WORDS, THAT CAN EITHER BE AMUSING OR SERIOUS. NOW MARIE KIDD SAYS THAT AN 
OXYMORON IS SOMEONE WHO GRADUATES FROM OCCIDENTAL COLLEGE, BUT SHE 
CAN SAY THAT BECAUSE THATS HER ALMA MATER. HOW MANY OTHER OCCY-AH-
PEOPLE DO WE HAVE HERE TODAY? DRY DRUNK SOUNDS LIKE THAT, A STRAIGHT 
CONTRADICTION IN TERMS. FOR HOW CAN SOMEONE BE BOTH DRUNK AND DRY, 
WHICH MEANS SOBER, AT THE SAME TIME?
	WHEN I ASKED HER WHAT SHE MEANT BY THE TERM DRY DRUNK, SISTER JUDY 
REPLIED THAT SOMEONE CAN BE IN RECOVERY AND STILL SUFFER FROM THE SAME 
COMPULSIVE, SELF-DESTRUCTIVE BEHAVIOR PATTERNS THAT THEY HAD WHEN THEY 
WERE DRINKING, ONLY WITHOUT THE BOOZE. ITS MORE THAN JUST FEELING THE 
CONSTANT CRAVING FOR A DRINK. A DRY DRUNK MAY HAVE FOUND SOME OTHER 
THING TO DO JUST AS COMPULSIVELY AS THEY USED TO PRACTICE DRINKING, SUCH 
AS GAMBLING, SMOKING, SHOPPING HAVING SEX OR BEING ANGRY. SOME ALCOHOLIC 
PEOPLE EVEN FOOL THEMSELVES INTO THINKING THAT THEY NEED OTHER DRUGS 
SUCH AS MARIJUANA TO HELP THEM KICK THE BOTTLE. 
	ONE OF THE TRUE COLLATERAL EFFECTS OF A HARD-DRINKING LIFESTYLE IS 
THE SHEER AMOUNT OF TIME IT TAKES TO STAY LOADED AND GET OVER HANGOVERS. 
ABSORBING ALCOHOL CAN BE VERY ABSORBING. WHEN A PERSON GETS SOBER, 
THERE IS SUDDENLY THIS BIG EXPANSE OF TIME STRETCHING BEFORE THEM, TIME 
THAT THEY USED TO SPEND CELEBRATING. AND A RECOVERING ALCOHOLIC WITH 
TIME ON HIS OR HER HANDS IS ALREADY IN BIG TROUBLE; THAT IS WHY THE WEEKLY 
COMMITMENT OF ATTENDING A 12-STEP GROUP IS SO IMPORTANT.
	NOW IVE BEEN TALKING ABOUT THE HARVEST CRUSADE MINISTRY QUITE A BIT 
IN THE LAST MONTH OR SO, BUT LET ME JUST SAY ONE MORE THING ABOUT IT: THERE 
WAS TRUE CHRISTIAN UNITY IN THAT MINISTRY, MORE STRONGLY SO THAN I HAVE 
EVER EXPERIENCED BEFORE. THE CRUSADES ARE NOT ABOUT BUILDING UP GREG 
LAURIES CHURCH OR ANY OTHER SINGLE CONGREGATION; THEY ARE ABOUT 
BUILDING UP THE BODY OF CHRIST. THEY ARE ABOUT HELPING GOD MAKE 
CHRISTIANS. THAT MESSAGE IS BOTH ON THE LINES AND BETWEEN THE LINES IN 
EVERYTHING THAT IS DONE DURING THE CRUSADES. MY BELIEF IS THAT EVERY 
DENOMINATION AND EVERY LOCAL CONGREGATION WOULD BE ABLE TO DO A BETTER 
JOB OF EVANGELISM IF IT DEMONSTRATED THE INTEGRITY THAT IS EVIDENT TROUGH 
THE HARVEST CRUSADE MINISTRY. I THINK THAT PEOPLE ARE SICK AND TIRED OF 
HEARING ABOUT ALL OF THE STUFF THAT WE USUALLY HEAR ABOUT FROM BIG 
DENOMINATIONS OR MEGA-MINISTRIES, STUFF LIKE DISPUTES OVER SOCIAL ISSUES, 
MONEY PROBLEMS OR LIFESTYLE SCANDALS AMONG PASTORS. HERE, THERE AND 
EVERYWHERE, PEOPLE ARE SEARCHING FOR THE GENUINE ARTICLE, THE REAL THING, 
CHRISTIANITY WITH INTEGRITY.
	LAST TUESDAY I WAS BLESSED BY GETTING A MESSAGE ON MY BEEPER. YOU 
MAY NOT LIKE PAGERS; YOU MAY NOT EVEN LIKE PHONE ANSWERING MACHINES, BUT 
OF YOU ARE AGAINST THESE THINGS, PLEASE GET OVER IT! NOW I HAVE TO SAY 
RIGHT AWAY THAT DRIVERS FIDDLING AROUND WITH THEIR CELL PHONES WHILE 
THEYRE SUPPOSED TO BE PAYING ATTENTION TO THE ROAD REALLY BUG MY GUTS. 
SO I GUESS THAT WE ALL HAVE OUR LIKES AND DISLIKES. 
	ANYWAY, I GOT TWO PAGES BACK TO BACK FROM THE SAME GLENDALE 
DIALING PREFIX. THERE WAS NO ANSWER AT THE FIRST NUMBER, BUT THE SECOND 
NUMBER WAS BUSY AND SO I DECIDED TO TRY AGAIN LATER. ON THE THIRD TRY I GOT 
A YOUNG MAN WHO HAD ATTENDED THE HARVEST CRUSADE, ONE OF THE PEOPLE 
WHO HAD COME FORWARD AT THE TIME OF THE INVITATION. WE HAD SENT HIM A 
FOLLOW-UP LETTER WHICH INCLUDED MY PAGER NUMBER, AND HE HAD TRIED IT SO 
THAT HE COULD ASK ME A QUESTION: WHAT DID I THINK OF 12-STEP GROUPS? I SAID 
THAT I THOUGHT THEY WERE A VERY EFFECTIVE FORM OF MINISTRY, AND WE HAD 
SEVERAL OF THEM MEETING AT OUR CHURCH EVERY WEEK. HE SAID THAT HEARING 
ME SAY THAT WAS A RELIEF TO HIM, FOR HE HAD BEEN IN RECOVERY FOR 6 YEARS 
AND CONSIDERED THE 12-STEP PROGRAM TO REALLY BE HIS CHURCH. BUT THEN, 
AFTER 6 YEARS OF SOBRIETY, HE HAD BEGUN TO HEAR THE CALL OF CHRIST IN HIS 
LIFE. PRAISE GOD! 	
	AND SO HE WENT TO THE HARVEST CRUSADE AND CAME FORWARD AT THE TIME 
OF THE INVITATION. DOWN THERE ON THAT BASEBALL FIELD, WITH OVER 4,000 
OTHERS WHO WILLINGLY ANSWERED THE INVITATION TO ACCEPT JESUS CHRIST, HE 
HAD GOTTEN A CRITICAL TURNOFF. A NOVICE CHRISTIAN COUNSELOR HAD TOLD HIM 
THAT HE DIDNT NEED THE 12-STEP PROGRAM; THAT HE ONLY NEEDED ONE STEP, AND 
THAT STEP IS JESUS CHRIST. I TOLD HIM THAT HE HAD BEEN GIVEN THE WRONG 
ADVICE. 12-STEP GROUPS AFFIRM GOD, THEY JUST LEAVE THE DEFINITION OF GOD A 
LITTLE VAGUE, AND ITS PERFECTLY ALRIGHT WITH GOD IF YOU PUT HIS NAME OR THE 
NAME OF JESUS CHRIST INTO THE 12-STEP FORMULA.
	NOT PLEASE UNDERSTAND--IM NOT SAYING THAT ANY AND ALL ANSWERS TO 
THE HUMAN SEARCH FOR GOD ARE EQUALLY VALID. I WOULD NOT RECOMMEND 
ANYONE TO STAY IN A CULT ONE MINUTE LONGER THAN THEY HAVE STAYED 
ALREADY. HOW TO YOU TELL IF IT IS A CULT? ITS VERY SIMPLE: CULTS IDOLIZE MEN; 
CHURCHES WORSHIP GOD. BUT EVEN A CULT OR A NEW AGE INTEREST GROUP CAN 
BE A STEPPING STONE ON THE WAY TO CHRISTIAN DISCIPLESHIP. WEVE GOT TO BE 
VERY CAREFUL IN WHAT WE CONDEMN, LEST WE UNCERCUT THE SUFFICIENCY OF THE 
BLOOD OF CHRIST. HOW DID JESUS PUT IT? DO NOT JUDGE ONE ANOTHER, SO THAT 
YOU YOURSELVES WILL NOT BE JUDGED. A SURVEY OF PEOPLE WHO JOINED NEW 
AGE MOVEMENTS REVEALED THAT THE VAST MAJORITY, OVER 75% OF THEM, WERE 
REACTING AGAINST A NEGATIVE EXPERIENCE THEY HAD HAD IN A CHRISTIAN 
CHURCH, AN EXPERIENCE OF BEING JUDGED BY PEOPLE NO HOLIER THAN THEY 
WERE, BUT WHO THOUGHT THEMSELVES HOLY.
	IN OUR SCRIPTURE FOR THIS MORNING, PAUL COMES AS CLEAN AS ANY 
CHRISTIAN CAN COME CLEAN. HE ADMITS TO EXPERIENCING THE FLUCTUATIONS OF 
FAITH. WHEN WE BECOME CHRISTIANS, WHEN WE ACCEPT JESUS CHRIST INTO OUR 
LIFE, WHAT HAPPENS IS USUALLY DRAMATIC AT FIRST, AND LESS DRAMATIC LATER 
ON. THE INITIAL EUPHORIA OF ACCEPTANCE WEARS OFF, AND THE HARD WORK OF 
GROWING IN CHRIST SETS IN. THE OLD-TIMERS USED TO SAY THAT WHEN SOMEONE 
RECEIVES JESUS AS LORD FOR THE FIRST TIME, SATAN SENSES THAT HES LOSING 
THEM AND GOES TO WORK ON THEM HARDER THAN EVER BEFORE. IN OTHER WORDS, 
BEING A CHRISTIAN DOES NOT TAKE AWAY TEMPTATION, ALTHOUGH WE WISH IT 
WOULD TAKE TEMPTATION AWAY. AMEN? FAITH FLUCTUATES; OUR TEMPERS WAX 
AND WANE; OUR SENSE OF BLESSEDNESS RISES AND FALLS. GOOD FRIENDS, THATS 
NORMAL; DONT WORRY ABOUT IT; DONT TRY TO OVERCOME IT; LET IT BE!
	ITS NOT GOING TOO FAR TO SAY THAT PAULS STRUGGLE AS DESCRIBED ON 
THE 7TH CHAPTER OF ROMANS IS THE CLASSIC STRUGGLE OF A PERSON IN 
RECOVERY. THEY CAN WILL WHAT IS RIGHT, BUT DO NOT FEEL ABLE TO DO IT. THEY 
MANAGE TO ACHIEVE EVIL RATHER THAN ACHIEVING GOOD. TRYING TO DO THE GOOD, 
THEY FIND IT TO BE A LAW THAT EVIL LIES CLOSE AT HAND. THEY FEEL ENSLAVED, 
BOUND WITHIN THEIR OWN BODIES BY A SENSE OF CRAVING, WHETHER IT IS A 
CRAVING FOR A DRINK OR A CRAVING FOR SOMETHING ELSE, EVEN THE CRAVING FOR 
A SPIRITUAL HIGH. THEY LITERALLY FEEL THAT THEIR INNER LIVES ARE A BATTLE 
ZONE, A ZONE OF WAR BETWEEN MIND AND BODY. DOES THIS RING ANY BELLS? IS 
ANYBODY GETTING THIS?
	I AM HERE TO TELL YOU THAT JESUS UNDERSTANDS THIS KIND OF INNER 
STRUGGLE. EVEN THE SON OF GOD WAS TORN BY THE AWESOME REQUIREMENTS OF 
HIS OWN MINISTRY AND AT THE VERY LAST, HE FELT FORSAKEN BY GOD. IF THE SON 
OF GOD HAD HIS LOW TIMES, THEN YOU OUGHT TO BE AT PEACE WITH HAVING YOUR 
OWN LOW TIMES AS WELL. YET AS SURELY AS IT IS DARKEST JUST BEFORE THE 
DAWN, SO GOD WILL SEND A PENETRATING RAY OF HOPE INTO THE DENSE GLOOM OF 
YOUR OWN SOUL-SEARCHING SELF-DOUBT. FOR WHEN WE SEARCH OURSELVES 
THOROUGHLY, THERE IS ONLY ONE CONCLUSION WE CAN REACH: WE DO NOT 
POSSESS THE RESOURCES TO SAVE OURSELVES. ONLY GOD CAN SAVE US! ONLY GOD 
CAN PROVIDE THE DIFFERENCE BETWEEN DEFEAT AND VICTORY, BETWEEN BLESSING 
AND CURSE, BETWEEN ETERNAL DEATH AND EVERLASTING LIFE. ONLY GOD CAN HELP 
US MAINTAIN OUR FORWARD MOMENTUM AS WE CROSS THE BRIDGE OF SALVATION 
THROUGH JESUS CHRIST. AND I DECLARE UNTO YOU THAT THIS MUCH HELP IS 
ENOUGH. AMEN.
</PRE>
