<A HREF="/SMUMC/index.html"><H2>Return to Sierra Madre UMC home page.</H2></A>
<P>
A SPIRITUAL MINDSET	SERMON BY REV. RICH LA SHURE
ROMANS 8.1-11	JULY 21, 1996

	I REALLY SHOULD HAVE SEEN IT COMING. THERE HAD TO BE A COLLISION OF 
SOME SORT BETWEEN US, SOONER OR LATER. WERE JUST SO DIFFERENT. I DID NOT 
SAY THAT I AM BETTER THAN HIM; ALL I SAID WAS THAT WE ARE DIFFERENT. 
	LAST MONDAY AFTERNOON WHEN WE PULLED IN AT OUR SMALL VACATION 
GETAWAY, A DOUBLEWIDE MANUFACTURED HOME IN THE DESERT SCRUB OF THE 
OWENS VALLEY, WE NOTICED THAT SOMETHING WAS WRONG. 
	WHEN WE WERE THERE LATE LAST SPRING, MY WIFE AND I SPENT A SOLID 
WEEK DIGGING, PLANTING AND SETTING UP DRIP IRRIGATION FOR AROUND 100 
DESERT NATIVE FLOWERS, SHRUBS AND SMALL TREES. KATHY HAS STUDIED THE 
FLORA OF THE CALIFORNIA DESERT, IS A MEMBER OF THE CALIFORNIA NATIVE PLANT 
SOCIETY, AND SHE HAS DONE A WONDERFUL JOB OF DESIGNING OUR LANDSCAPE 
PLAN UP THERE. EVERY PLANT, FROM THE TALLEST COTTONWOOD TREE TO THE 
SMALLEST PENSTEMON, IS THERE FOR A REASON. SOMEDAY OUR TWO INCENSE 
CEDAR TREES WILL BE MIGHTY LIKE THE ONES IN THE HIGHLAND FORESTS OF THE 
SIERRA NEVADAS. THERE IS AN UPPER MOJAVE DESERT GARDEN, A RIVERINE 
GARDEN AND A PINYON-JUNIPER WOODLAND GARDEN. BY AND LARGE, EVERYTHING 
IS DOING FINE, EXCEPT FOR A FEW DOGWOOD CUTTINGS THAT DIDNT SURVIVE THE 
UNSEASONABLY HOT DAYS OF JUNE.
	BUT SOME TIME DURING THE LAST MONTH WE GOT VANDALIZED. SOMEONE HAD 
COME ALONG AND JERKED ABOUT TEN OF THE BUSHES IN OUR PINYON-JUNIPER ZONE 
OUT OF THE GROUND, LEAVING THE ROOT BALLS TO DESICCATE AND DIE IN THE 
DESERT SUN. ALL IN ALL, THE DAMAGE WAS WORTH ABOUT $100 PLUS LABOR. RIGHT 
AWAY I THOUGHT OF KARYO, AN 8-YEAR-OLD BOY WHOSE FAMILY LIVES THREE 
DOORS TO THE NORTH OF US. KARYO AND HIS FRIENDS LIKE TO RIDE BMX BIKES AND 
ESPECIALLY JUMP THEM OVER SMALL OBSTACLES. HE HAD COMMENCED USING THE 
FRONT STRIP OF OUR LOT FOR HIS BIKE JUMP ZONE, IN THE AREA WHICH IS 
TECHNICALLY A COUNTY EASEMENT. HIS BIKE JUMPING HAD THRASHED ONE OF THE 
LARGE RABBITBRUSH BUSHES WHICH WERE PART OF NATURES ORIGINAL 
LANDSCAPING. LAST TIME I HAD ASKED KARYO AND HIS FRIEND NOT TO RIDE THEIR 
BIKES THROUGH THE BUSHES, TRYING TO REASON WITH THEM AND NOT WANTING TO 
TAKE THE MATTER TO A HIGHER AUTHORITY.
	SO WHEN I SAW THE DEAD PLANTS THAT WE HAD CARINGLY PLANTED ALONG 
WITH THREE MORE RABBITBRUSH BUSHES LOOKING THE WORSE FOR WEAR, I 
WALKED OVER TO KARYOS HOUSE TO SPEAK WITH HIS MOTHER. I WAS NOT 
ACCUSATORY, JUST WANTING TO KNOW IF HE HAD SEEN ANYONE TEARING UP OUR 
YARD. HE SAID NO, BUT HIS MOM SENSED SOMETHING AND TOLD HIM THAT SHE 
WOULD ASK HER HUSBAND TO COME OVER AND SPEAK WITH ME ABOUT IT LATER.
	THAT WAS ALL FINE, BUT LATER ON, AS PRESIDENT HARRY TRUMAN MIGHT 
HAVE SAID, THE FERTILIZER HIT THE VENTILATOR. RIGHT HERE I NEED TO REMIND YOU 
ABOUT JOE, OUR NEXT DOOR NEIGHBOR FROM HELL. THE NAME HAS BEEN CHANGED 
TO PROTECT THE GUILTY. FROM DAY ONE JOE HAS BEEN A MILD BUT PERSISTENT 
PAIN IN THE KEISTER TO US. HE IS CLEARLY ADDICTED TO ALCOHOL AND NICOTINE 
DUE TO HIS CONTINUAL OUTDOOR INGESTING OF THESE SUBSTANCES IN VARIOUS 
FORMS RANGING FROM TALL COCKTAILS TO BEERS TO HANDROLLED CIGARETTES TO 
SNUFF. HE IS ALSO A COLLECTOR OF OLD VEHICLES AND LEAVES SEVERAL OF THEM 
SCATTERED ABOUT HIS PROPERTY AT ALL TIMES LIKE LOOSE POCKET CHANGE. SOME 
OF THEM RUN AND SOME DONT. HIS FLEET INCLUDES THREE--NO, MAKE THAT FOUR 
PICKUP TRUCKS, A PASSENGER SEDAN, A SMALL SPORTSCAR, A SPEEDBOAT, A 
TRAVEL TRAILER, TWO MOTORCYCLES AND A THREE-WHEELER WITH A VW ENGINE, 
PLUS SEVERAL CAMPER SHELLS AND ONE HUMONGOUS CABOVER CAMPER WHICH HE 
LEAVES ON THE GROUND. LAST YEAR WE REJOICED TO LEARN THAT HE WAS 
PLANNING TO BUILD A GARAGE TO HOUSE ALL OF HIS TOYS. THEN A MONSTER 
STRUCTURE MEASURING 15 FEET HIGH BY 1,000 SQUARE FEET FLOOR SPACE WAS 
ERECTED, MORE LIKE A CALTRANS EQUIPMENT SHED THAN A GARAGE, BLOTTING OUT 
A GOOD THIRD OF OUR VIEW OF THE SIERRAS TO THE WEST. WE REMINDED 
OURSELVES THAT THIS WASNT PASADENA, AND WE HAD NO SAY ABOUT WHAT A 
NEIGHBOR CAN BUILD IN YOUR VIEW. 	
	OK--BUT THEN JOE STILL DIDNT PUT HIS JUNK IN THE GARAGE! HE LIKES TO 
KEEP THE FLOOR CLEAR FOR ENGINE OVERHAULS, YOU SEE. OH, AND ONE MORE 
THING, THIS MAN KEEPS A BARKING, PEOPLE-CHASING DOG THAT IS THE TRUE 
TERROR OF THE NEIGHBORHOOD.
	THATS BACKGROUND TO WHAT HAPPENED LAST MONDAY. WHEN LITTLE 
KARYO, WHO IS NO RELATION TO HIM, FIBBED AND SAID THAT I HAD YELLED AT HIM, 
OUR NEIGHBOR JOE BLEW HIS TOP AND STARTED READING ME THE RIOT ACT. HE 
HYPERVENTILATED FOR A GOOD 40 MINUTES, AND I STOOD TOE TO TOE WITH HIM, LET 
HIM KNOW WHEN HE WAS OUT OF LINE, INSISTED ON HAVING MY SAY IN THE DISPUTE 
AND FINALLY WALKED HIM BACK TO HIS HOUSE TO SIMMER DOWN. OF COURSE, THE 
ISSUE ABOUT THE THRASHED PLANTS WAS ONLY THE ONE ON THE SURFACE. 
LURKING UNDERNEATH WAS THE YAWNING CHASM OF JUST HOW DIFFERENT WE ARE 
FROM EACH OTHER, AND HOW HE IS A FULL-TIMER UP THERE AND I AM ONLY A PART, 
PART-TIMER. BASICALLY HE RESENTS ME BECAUSE I LIVE IN TWO PLACES, EVEN 
THOUGH I ONLY OWN ONE OF THEM. WE CAN PICK OUR FRIENDS, BUT WE SURE CANT 
PICK OUR NEIGHBORS.
	I WAS VERY GLAD THAT THE LORD BLESSED ME TO MAINTAIN MY COMPOSURE 
THROUGHOUT AND NOT TRY TO GIVE AS GOOD AS I GOT. ACTUALLY I THINK IT WILL 
PROVE HELPFUL THAT JOE GOT HIS GRIPES OFF HIS CHEST. IT SURE WOULDNT HAVE 
HELPED FOR THIS FOUL STUFF TO HAVE SIMMERED ANY LONGER. NOW I AM NOT SO 
NAIVE TO THINK THAT WELL NOW BECOME THE BEST OF BUDDIES. THATS NOT 
POSSIBLE BECAUSE I POLITELY DECLINED JOES OFFER OF A DRINK LAST YEAR AND 
TOLD HIM I HAD TAKEN THE PLEDGE. HIS BUDDIES DRINK, PERIOD. BUT BY AND BY, 
THINGS WILL PROBABLY BE A LITTLE BETTER NOW THAT THE AIR HAS BEEN CLEARED.
	THE PROVERBS OF THE HEBREW SCRIPTURES TEACH US THAT A MAN WITHOUT 
SELF-CONTROL IS LIKE A CITY BROKEN INTO AND LEFT WITHOUT WALLS. (PROVERBS 
25.28) WHAT A FANTASTIC IMAGE, AND HOW WELL IT APPLIES TO MY NEIGHBOR. AND 
ANOTHER: MAKE NO FRIENDSHIP WITH A MAN GIVEN TO ANGER, NOR GO WITH A 
WRATHFUL MAN, LEST YOU LEARN HIS WAYS AND ENTANGLE YOURSELF IN A SNARE.  
(PROVERBS 22.24-25) ANOTHER: HE WHO IS SLOW TO ANGER HAS GREAT 
UNDERSTANDING, BUT HE WHO HAS A HASTY TEMPER EXALTS FOLLY. (PROVERBS 
14.29) ONE MORE: A SOFT ANSWER TURNS AWAY WRATH, BUT A HARSH WORD STIRS 
UP ANGER.  (PROVERBS 15.1)
	YESTERDAY THERE WAS AN AMAZING SET OF STATISTICS FROM A GEORGE 
BARNA POLL PRINTED IN THE RELIGION SECTION OF THE NEWSPAPER. THE ONE THAT 
STRUCK ME THE HARDEST IS THAT ALTHOUGH 90% OF AMERICANS OWN A BIBLE, 
ONLY ABOUT 20% OF THEM READ THE BIBLE REGULARLY. ONE OF THE REASONS 
MOST OFTEN GIVEN FOR THIS LOW BIBLE READING RATE WAS THAT THE FOLK DIDNT 
SEE THE RELEVANCE OF THE BIBLE FOR DAILY LIFE. IF THATS TRUE, THEN THE FAULT 
BELONGS TO PREACHERS, PASTORS AND BIBLE TEACHERS FOR NOT DOING THEIR 
JOB MORE THOROUGHLY.
	I SAY UNTO YOU THAT THIS SECTION OF PAULS LETTER TO THE CHURCH AT 
ROME HAS SOME OF THE MOST PROFOUND SIGNIFICANCE FOR EVERYDAY LIFE THAT 
YOU CAN FIND ANYWHERE IN THE ENTIRE BIBLE APART FROM THE ACTUAL 
TEACHINGS OF JESUS HIMSELF. FOR IN ROMANS PAUL LAYS OUT THE THEOLOGY OF 
SALVATION MORE CLEARLY AND WITH GREATER DETAIL THAN HE DOES ANYWHERE 
ELSE.
	IN OUR SCRIPTURE FOR TODAY, PAUL DESCRIBES THE MINDSET OF A 
CHRISTIAN. I CALL IT A SPIRITUAL MINDSET. NOW MINDSET IS NOT A BIBLICAL TERM. 
YOU WONT FIND THE WORD MINDSET IN YOUR CONCORDANCE. ITS ACTUALLY A 
PSYCHOLOGICAL TERM WHICH REFERS TO THE PRE-CONDITION OF A CERTAIN 
COLORING ATTITUDE, A PRE-SUPPOSITION WHICH PEOPLE CARRY AROUND WITH 
THEM WHEREVER THEY GO. 
	FOR A MINUTE LETS THINK ABOUT DIFFERENT MINDSETS. HAVE YOU EVER 
KNOWN SOMEONE WHO ALWAYS SEEMED TO BE FEELING SORRY FOR SOMETHING OR 
SOMEONE ELSE? ITS NOT ALWAYS BECAUSE THERES SOMETHING TO BE SORRY 
ABOUT; IT MAY JUST BE THAT THEY HAVE A PITYING MINDSET, WHICH IS A SUBTLE 
WAY FOR THEM TO FEEL SUPERIOR, SO AS TO COMPENSATE FOR FEELING INFERIOR. 
	OR WHAT ABOUT SOMEONE WITH A PERFECTIONIST MINDSET? SUCH PEOPLE 
ARE THE WORLDS GREATEST FAULTFINDERS, NITPICKERS AND FUN-SPOILERS. HOW 
THEY BUG US! SOMEONE WITH A MINDSET FOR MONEY CANT HAVE THE SIMPLEST 
CONVERSATION WITH ANOTHER PERSON WITHOUT LOOKING FOR THE WAY IT CAN 
PROFIT THEM PERSONALLY. IN THIS ENDLESS QUEST FOR MORE AND MORE MONEY, 
THEIR SOULS ARE DRIVEN TO BANKRUPTCY. AND WHAT ABOUT AN ANGRY MINDSET?
	I THINK THAT IT WOULD GREATLY HELP EACH AND EVERY ONE OF US TO 
SEARCH OUR THOUGHTS AND TRY TO DETERMINE WHETHER WE HAVE ANY SUCH 
COLORING ATTITUDES WHICH WE CARRY AROUND WITH US. WHAT IS YOUR MINDSET? 
IS IT POSSIBLE TO CHANGE A PERSONS MINDSET, OR IS A MIND, ONCE SET, SET 
FOREVER?
	PAUL TEACHES US THAT THERE ARE BASICALLY ONLY TWO CATEGORIES OF 
MINDSETS: CARNAL AND SPIRITUAL. ALL THE DIFFERENT CASTS OF MIND BOIL DOWN 
TO ONE OR THE OTHER OF THESE TWO. OUR MINDS ARE EITHER SET UPON THINGS OF 
THE FLESH, OR THEY ARE SET UPON THE THINGS OF THE SPIRIT. ITS REALLY THAT 
SIMPLE. 
	IN A RECENT ISSUE OF GUIDEPOSTS MAGAZINE, I READ A WONDERFUL LETTER 
TO THE EDITOR. IN IT THE PERSON COMPARED CONTEMPORARY LIFE TO A DRIVERS 
EDUCATION CLASS. WHAT IF, HE ASKED, THE STUDENTS IN DRIVERS ED WERE 
TAUGHT TO DRIVE ON THE RIGHT SIDE OF THE ROAD, UNLESS, OF COURSE, YOU WISH 
TO DRIVE ON THE LEFT...MOST PEOPLE DRIVE ON THE RIGHT SIDE OF THE ROAD, BUT 
SOME PREFER TO DRIVE ON THE LEFT SIDE OF THE ROAD...IF YOU DECIDE TO DO THIS, 
ALWAYS WEAR A SEAT BELT...SEAT BELTS SAVE LIVES. OF COURSE, WE WOULD 
NEVER TOLERATE SUCH AN APPROACH TO DRIVER EDUCATION, NOW WOULD WE? BUT 
ISNT IT POSSIBLY TRUE THAT WE DO TOLERATE SUCH AN APPROACH TO OTHER 
KINDS OF EDUCATION, SUCH AS SEX EDUCATION OR EVEN RELIGIOUS EDUCATION?
	NOW MAYBE THE AUTOMOTIVE ANALOGY JUST SOUNDS WAY TOO SIMPLE FOR 
YOU. SOME MAY ASK, ISNT THERE MORE OF A GRAY AREA IN LIFE THAN THAT? NOT 
ACCORDING TO PAUL THERE ISNT. LETS COMPARE THE SPIRITUAL MINDSET AND THE 
CARNAL MINDSET. SIX COMPARISONS:
	1. THE CARNAL MINDSET LEADS TO DEATH; 
		THE SPIRITUAL MINDSET LEADS TO LIFE.
	2. THE CARNAL MINDSET IS HOSTILE TO GOD; 
		THE SPIRITUAL MINDSET LOVES GOD AND PLEASES GOD.
	3. THE CARNAL MINDSET IS IN BONDAGE TO THE LAW OF SIN AND DEATH;
		THE SPIRITUAL MINDSET IS FREE FROM THE LAW OF SIN AND DEATH.
	4. THE CARNAL MINDSET DOES NOT KNOW CHRIST;
		THE SPIRITUAL MINDSET KNOWS CHRIST AS LORD AND SAVIOR.
	5. THE CARNAL MINDSET WILL DIE FOREVER;
		THE SPIRITUAL MINDSET WILL BE RESURRECTED WITH CHRIST.
	6. THE CARNAL MINDSET IS CONDEMNED;
		THE SPIRITUAL MINDSET IS PARDONED.
	I WOULD SAY THAT THIS IS PRETTY MUCH AN EITHER-OR SITUATION, WOULDNT 
YOU? AND WHICH MINDSET WOULD YOU PREFER TO HAVE? WHICH MINDSET OFFERS 
US THE BETTER DEAL? WHICH ONE HAS SUPERIOR BENEFITS? WHICH ONE? THE 
SPIRITUAL MINDSET, THATS RIGHT. NOW WERE GETTING SOMEWHERE.
	IF ANY REASONABLE PERSON WOULD CHOOSE THE SPIRITUAL MINDSET OVER 
THE CARNAL MINDSET, THEN WHATS THE NEXT STEP? HOW DO WE OBTAIN THE 
SPIRITUAL MINDSET? IS IT POSSIBLE TO LOSE THE SPIRITUAL MINDSET ONCE WE HAVE 
OBTAINED IT? WHAT HAPPENS THEN?
	THE KEY TO THIS WHOLE MINDSET THEOLOGY IS THE PAULINE BAPTISMAL 
FORMULA IN CHRIST. ITS RIGHT THERE IN VERSE ONE: THERE IS THEREFORE NOW 
NO CONDEMNATION FOR THOSE WHO ARE IN CHRIST JESUS.--MEANING BAPTIZED. 
THIS IS THE TRUE POWER OF HOLY BAPTISM, THE SACRAMENT OF GODS INFINITE 
ACCEPTANCE OF US THROUGH THE MINISTRY OF JOHN THE BAPTIST AND JESUS THE 
CHRIST. BAPTISM IS A DIVINE ACT OF PARDON, AN INITIATIVE ON GODS PART, AN 
UNCONDITIONAL OFFER OF NEW LIFE. WHEN WE RECEIVE GODS GIFT OF BAPTISM WE 
ARE INITIATED INTO THE FAMILY OF THE REDEEMED AND BLESSED CHILDREN OF THE 
HEAVENLY FATHER.
	SO ONCE AGAIN, TO BORROW THE PHRASE OF ROSS PEROT, ITS THAT SIMPLE. 
IN ORDER TO RECEIVE A SPIRITUAL MINDSET, WE SIMPLY NEED TO ACCEPT THE FACT 
THAT WE ARE ACCEPTED BY GOD, AND CLAIM THE POWER AND THE MEANING OF OUR 
OWN BAPTISM. ONCE BAPTIZED, ITS POSSIBLE FOR A CHRISTIAN TO SWERVE AWAY 
FROM THE SPIRITUAL MINDSET BACK TOWARD THE DISCREDITED CARNAL MINDSET 
WHICH THE SPIRITUAL MINDSET CAME TO REPLACE. IN ORDER TO GUARD AGAINST 
THIS TENDENCY TO DRIFT OFF COURSE, ITS IMPORTANT THAT WE ENGAGE FAITHS 
FORWARD GEAR AND DRIVE ON THE RIGHT SIDE OF THE ROAD. THIS MEANS THAT WE 
MUST, TO USE THE EXPRESSION OF BROTHER THEODORE, PRACTICE THE PRESENCE 
OF CHRIST. 
	IN WHATEVER LIFE SITUATIONS WE MIGHT FIND OURSELVES, THERE IS A CHRIST-
LIKE WAY TO BEHAVE AND THERE IS A CHRIST-DENYING WAY TO BEHAVE. IN ORDER 
TO FIND THE CHRIST-LIKE WAY TO BEHAVE, WE MUST SINCERELY PRAY FOR THE MIND 
OF CHRIST TO BE EXPRESSED THROUGH OUR MINDS, OUR WORDS AND OUR ACTIONS. 
HOW WOULD JESUS HAVE REACTED IN THIS SITUATION? WHAT WOULD HE HAVE SAID? 
HOW WOULD HE HAVE BLESSED THOSE WHO PERSECUTED HIM? HOW WOULD HE 
HAVE FORGIVEN THOSE WHO WRONGED HIM? NOW WERE NOT GOING TO BECOME 
SKILLED AT THIS KIND OF CHRIST-LIKENESS OVERNIGHT, BUT I CAN GUARANTEE YOU 
ONE THING: WE GET BETTER AT IT WITH PRACTICE. I THANK GOD FOR SENDING ME MY 
AWFUL NEIGHBOR UP NORTH, FOR HE DEMONSTRATES THE CARNAL MINDSET, AND 
WITH HIS EXAMPLE, I AM HELPED TO WORK ON MY OWN SPIRITUAL MINDSET.
	I CLOSE WITH THIS VERSE, A PRAYER REALLY, WRITTEN BY AMY CARMICHAEL. 
MAY IT BE A PRAYER FOR YOU TO USE DURING THE ROUGH TIMES AND THE TENSE 
MOMENTS OF LIFE, SO THAT YOU MAY ACQUIRE AND MAINTAIN A SPIRITUAL MINDSET. 
ITS IMPORTANT TO THINK OF TREES HERE, STURDY TREES, STANDING STRONG 
AGAINST THE WIND WITH THICK TRUNKS, STOUT BRANCHES AND DEEP, SOIL-GRIPPING 
ROOTS.
		GOD OF THE GALLANT TREES,
		GIVE TO US FORTITUDE;
		GIVE AS THOU GIVEST TO THESE
		VALOROUS HARDIHOOD. 
		WE ARE THE TREES OF THY PLANTING, O GOD.
		NOW LET THE LIFE-SAP RUN
		CLEAN THROUGH OUR EVERY VEIN.
		PERFECT THAT THOU HAST BEGUN,
		GOD OF THE SUN AND RAIN:
		THOU WHO DOST MEASURE THE WEIGHT OF THE WIND,
		FIT US FOR STRESS AND FOR STRAIN.
	LET GODS PEOPLE SAY AMEN.

<A HREF="/SMUMC/index.html"><H2>Return to Sierra Madre UMC home page.</H2></A>
</PRE>
</BODY>
</HTML>

</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT23-B01-233</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA063-000368-B029-169</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.magicdragon.com:80/SMUMC/Victorious7.28.96.html 206.149.251.176 19970112054722 text/html 14006
