Content-length: 13822
</DOCHDR>
<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Victorious, July 28, 1996</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<META NAME="Author" CONTENT="Rich La Shure">
<META NAME="Keywords" CONTENT="Olympics Kelli Strug prayer religion 
                               justification Jesus Christ
                               Christianity Methodist salvation">
<META NAME="expiration" CONTENT="December 31, 1996">
<BODY>
<P>
<A HREF="/SMUMC/index.html"><H2>Return to Sierra Madre UMC home page.</H2></A>

<PRE>
VICTORIOUS	SERMON BY REV. RICH LA SHURE
ROMANS 8.31-39	JULY 28, 1996

	IT HAS BEEN A GREAT WEEK OF OLYMPIC COMPETITION, LITERALLY THE BEST 
TELEVISION IN THE KNOWN WORLD EVERY SINGLE NIGHT. THE OLYMPICS ARE SO 
GOOD THAT ITS EASY TO GET HOOKED AND JUST LET AN ENTIRE EVENING SLIP AWAY 
UNNOTICED. I AM DISCIPLINING MYSELF TO GET UP AND DO THINGS AROUND THE 
HOUSE OR IN THE GARAGE, LEAVING THE TV ON SO THAT I CAN COME BACK AND 
CHECK UP ON IT FROM TIME TO TIME. I FIND THAT ITS EASIEST TO BREAK AWAY WHEN 
MENS BASKETBALL IS ON, FOR THE SO-CALLED DREAM TEAM DISGUSTS ME. THIS 
BUNCH OF OVERSIZED, GROSSLY OVERPAID WHINGERS WITH THEIR PARTIES AND 
THEIR LIMOUSINES AND THEIR ROOMS AT THE OMNI HOTEL INSTEAD OF AT THE 
OLYMPIC VILLAGE ARE REALLY GIVING THE UNITED STATES A CAULIFLOWER EAR. 
WHATS A WHINGER? OH, THATS FROM THE EXPRESSIVE AUSTRALIAN VERB TO 
WHINGE. TO WHINGE IS TO WHINE AND TO CRINGE AT THE SAME TIME. AUSSIE 
PARENTS OF THE TOUGH-LOVE SCHOOL TELL THEIR CHILDREN NOT TO WHINGE, 
PERIOD. MOTHERS, DONT LET YOUR SONS GROW UP TO BE NBA PLAYERS.
	I HAVE ONE MORE CRITICISM ABOUT THE OLYMPICS TO GET OFF MY CHEST. IM 
REALLY SICK AND TIRED OF THOSE ADS FOR REEBOK SHOES WHICH ALWAYS 
CONCLUDE WITH THE UNBELIEVABLY ARROGANT WORDS THIS IS MY PLANET. ONE 
OF THE ADS EVEN WENT SO FAR AS TO HAVE A MANS VOICE GROWLING, YOU DONT 
WIN SILVER...YOU LOSE GOLD...THIS IS MY PLANET. NOW THATS AN ATTITUDE THAT I 
AM SURE THE DREAM TEAM CAN GET BEHIND! 
	WHEN BELARUSSIAN GYMNAST VITALY SCHERBO FINISHED THIRD BEHIND LI 
XIAOSHUANG OF CHINA AND ALEXEI NEMOV OF RUSSIA, IT JUST WASNT GOOD 
ENOUGH FOR HIM. SCHERBO IS THE MAN WHOSE WIFE NEARLY DIED IN A CAR 
ACCIDENT LAST CHRISTMAS AND WAS IN A COMA FOR OVER ONE MONTH. FEARING 
THAT SHE MIGHT DIE, HE RETIRED FROM TRAINING TO BE AT HER BEDSIDE. WHEN SHE 
REGAINED CONSCIOUSNESS SHE MADE HIM PROMISE TO RETURN TO GYMNASTICS. 
THATS A GREAT STORY, AND IT REALLY ADDED SOME DRAMA TO THE COMPETITION. 
BUT WHEN SCHERBO LEFT THE AWARDS PLATFORM, HE DISDAINFULLY REMOVED THE 
BRONZE MEDAL FROM HIS NECK. LATER ON, HE HUNG THE BLAME ON HIS WIFE WHOM 
HE SAID WAS WAITING FOR A GOLD MEDAL. IN MY FAMILY, WE DONT KNOW MEDALS 
OF ANOTHER COLOR. ARE THOSE THE WORDS OF A FIERCE COMPETITOR WITH MUCH 
TO BE GRATEFUL FOR, OR JUST A POOR SPORT? YOU TELL ME. I HOPE HIS REEBOKS 
GIVE HIM TOENAIL FUNGUS!
	OF COURSE, AFTER LAST TUESDAY EVENING AMERICA NOW HAS A NEW 
OLYMPIC HERO: KERRI STRUG OF THE WOMENS GYMNASTICS TEAM. HER PICTURE 
WILL BE ON MORE MAGAZINE COVERS THAN MICHAEL JORDANS IN THE DAYS AND 
WEEKS AHEAD. STRUGS VALIANT PERFORMANCE IN THE VAULT EVENT WILL BE 
FOREVER ETCHED IN OUR MEMORY. BY NOW YOUVE PROBABLY HEARD THE STORY 
SEVERAL TIMES ALREADY, BUT LET ME JUST REVIEW THE DETAILS: GOING INTO THE 
OPTIONAL PORTION OF THE COMPETITION, THE UNITED STATES TEAM WAS A CLOSE 
SECOND BEHIND RUSSIA, WHOSE COACH HAD ALREADY LED THE RUSSIAN MEN TO A 
TEAM GOLD MEDAL. IT LOOKED LIKE THE OLD RED MACHINE WAS STILL IN FINE 
WORKING ORDER. LED BY WILLOWY SVETLANA CHORKINA, THE RUSSIANS WERE 
STRONG IN EVERY ONE OF THE FIRST FIVE ROTATIONS. FINALLY, IT CAME DOWN TO 
THE SIXTH AND FINAL ROTATION AND MIRACULOUSLY, THE AMERICANS WERE AHEAD 
BY NEARLY A FULL POINT. THUS THE STAGE WAS SET FOR WHAT WAS ONE OF THE 
GREATEST AMERICAN VICTORIES IN THE ENTIRE HISTORY OF THE OLYMPICS.
	THERE ARE SEVEN WOMEN ON A GYMNASTICS TEAM, AND THE LOWEST SCORE 
IN EACH ROTATION IS NOT COUNTED IN THE TALLY. OUR TEAMS FINAL EVENT WAS 
THE VAULT, AND THE RUSSIAN TEAMS FINAL EVENT WAS THE FLOOR EXERCISE. IN 
THE WOMENS VAULT EACH ATHLETE GETS TWO SHOTS, COUNTING ONLY THE HIGHER 
OF THE TWO SCORES. ONE BY ONE, THESE YOUNG WOMEN CAME BLAZING DOWN THE 
RUNWAY, LEAPED, SOARED, TUMBLED AND TWISTED WITH UNBELIEVABLE GRACE, 
AND CAME DOWN FOR A LANDING. THEIR VAULTS WERE GREAT, BUT NONE OF THEM 
STUCK THEIR LANDING--THEY WERE SO PUMPED UP THAT THEY KEPT OVER-
ROTATING, WHICH CAUSED THEM TO MAKE A STEP OR HOP AT THE END. DOMINIQUE 
DAWES TOOK A HUGE STEP, AND IT COST HER A NEAR-PERFECT SCORE. BUT THE 
SCORES WERE STILL GOOD UNTIL THE OTHER DOMINIQUE, DOMINIQUE MOCEANU OF 
HOLLYWOOD, CA CAME UP. MEANWHILE THE RUSSIANS WERE CRANKING OUT 9.7S 
OUT OF A POSSIBLE 10 ON THE FLOOR EXERCISE. A FLOOR EXERCISE TAKES 70 TO 90 
SECONDS TO COMPLETE WHILE A VAULT IS OVERWITH IN LESS THAN 10 SECONDS. 
	MOCEANU UNDER-ROTATED AND FELL ON HER FIRST VAULT, SITTING DOWN ON 
THE LANDING. THE NBC ANALYSTS FIGURED THAT A 9.7 MARK WOULD CLINCH THE 
GOLD MEDAL FOR AMERICA. SHE STILL HAD ANOTHER CHANCE. THEN, INCREDIBLY, 
SHE FELL DOWN AGAIN! HER TOP SCORE WAS A DISMAL 9.2, NO HELP AT ALL. THE 
LAST VAULTER FOR THE U.S. WAS 19-YEAR-OLD KERRI STRUG OF HOUSTON, TX. ONCE 
MORE, THE PROJECTED FIGURES CAME UP--A 9.6 AND CHANGE WOULD CLINCH THE 
GOLD--WELL WITHIN HER CAPABILITY. DOWN THE RUNWAY CAME KELLI STRUG, SHE 
HIT, SHE SOARED, SHE FLIPPED, SHE TWISTED--AND SHE SAT DOWN ON HER LANDING! 
THEN THE HUGE CROWD OF OVER 30,000 SPECTATORS ALL GASPED AS THEY SAW 
HER FAVOR HER LEFT FOOT AS SHE WALKED BACK TO THE START. STRUG WAS 
INJURED! 
	OVER ON THE FLOOR EXERCISE THE RUSSIANS HAD JUST CRANKED OUT 
ANOTHER BIG SCORE. TWO RUSSIANS WERE STILL TO GO, THEIR VERY BEST WOMEN 
ON THAT EVENT. A VAULTER IS ONLY ALLOWED 45 SECONDS BETWEEN VAULTS, OR 
ELSE THE SECOND SCORE WILL NOT BE COUNTED. STRUGS FALL GAVE HER A MARK 
IN THE 9.1 RANGE--THE TEAMS LOWEST. IF SHE COULD NOT DO BETTER THAN 
MOCEANUS 9.2, IT WOULD HAVE TO BE COUNTED IN THE TOTAL. IF THAT HAPPENED 
AND THE TWO RUSSIANS LANDED 9.9S, THEY COULD TAKE AWAY THE GOLD. 
	SO IT WAS LITERALLY CRUNCH TIME. BELA KAROLI, WHOSE WIFE MARTA IS THE 
OFFICIAL U.S. WOMENS COACH BUT WHO IS THE DE FACTO COACH FROM BEHIND THE 
PERSONAL COACHES BARRIER, MADE THE CRUCIAL DECISION OF A FIELD 
COMMANDER. HE SHOUTED, WE NEED ANOTHER, KERRI! AND THE LIMPING KERRI 
STRUG SHOUTED BACK, I WILL! I WILL! I WILL! AT THAT POINT, NO ONE KNEW THE 
SEVERITY OF THE INJURY SHE HAD SUFFERED ON THE FIRST VAULT. ALL STRUG KNEW 
WAS THAT SHE COULDNT FEEL HER LEFT FOOT REAL WELL.
	YOUVE GOT TO UNDERSTAND THAT ALL OVER THE WORLD, YOUNG WOMEN 
GYMNASTS LITERALLY REVERE BELA KAROLI, THE ROMANIAN OLYMPIC COACH WHO 
LED HIS TEAM TO GOLD IN THE 84 AND 88 GAMES. HIS STRICT TRAINING METHODS 
ARE CONTROVERSIAL, BUT HE DELIVERS THE GOODS. KAROLI DEFECTED TO THE USA 
AND HIS SUPERSTAR GYMNAST NADIA COMANICI FOLLOWED HIM. HE HAS TURNED THE 
AMERICAN PROGRAM AROUND, AND CONSIDERS THE CURRENT TEAM TO BE THE BEST 
GROUP OF ATHLETES HE HAS EVER COACHED. WHEN BELA KAROLI SAYS THAT HE 
NEEDS ANOTHER VAULT, THERE IS NO FEMALE GYMNAST ANYWHERE WHO WOULD 
NOT PULL HERSELF OFF A TRAINERS TABLE TO GIVE IT TO HIM.
	FOR A MOMENT, IT WAS AS THOUGH TIME WERE SUSPENDED IN THE TENSION OF 
ANTICIPATION. KELLI STRUG SAYS THAT SHE PRAYED TO GOD FOR HELP. THEN DOWN 
THE RUNWAY SHE CAME, BLASTED OFF, AND STUCK HER LANDING--ON ONE FOOT! 
HER LEFT FOOT BARELY TOUCHED THE MAT UPON IMPACT. SHE LIFTED HER ARMS 
UPWARD IN THE GESTURE OF VICTORY, TURNED AROUND, AND QUICKLY COLLAPSED 
IN PAIN. THE SCORE FOR HER VAULT WAS A LITTLE OVER 9.7, AND IT CLINCHED THE 
GOLD MEDAL FOR THE AMERICANS FOR THE FIRST TIME IN OLYMPIC HISTORY.
	WHEN I SAW STRUG HIT HER SECOND VAULT, I LOST EMOTIONAL CONTROL. 
PROBABLY SOME OF YOU LOST IT, TOO. I WAS SO PROUD OF HER AND THE OTHER 
WOMEN ON OUR TEAM WHICH IS NOW THE WORLDS BEST. AND I WAS SO TOUCHED BY 
THE COURAGE IT TOOK FOR HER TO EVEN ATTEMPT THAT SECOND VAULT. LATER ON, 
X-RAYS REVEALED NO BROKEN BONES BUT AN MRI FOUND TWO TORN LIGAMENTS IN 
STRUGS LEFT ANKLE. SO SHE SACRIFICED HER CHANCE AT AN INDIVIDUAL MEDAL IN 
ORDER TO BRING ONE HOME FOR HER TEAM.
	BY THE NEXT MORNING THE SECOND-GUESSERS AND MONDAY MORNING 
QUARTERBACKS FIGURED OUT THAT IN RETROSPECT, THE AMERICANS WOULD HAVE 
STILL WON THE GOLD WITHOUT STRUGS SECOND VAULT. OR SO THEY CONJECTURED, 
USING THE FINAL TWO SCORES OF THE RUSSIANS FOR COMPARISON. BUT REMEMBER: 
THOSE RUSSIAN SCORES HAD NOT YET BEEN POSTED WHEN STRUG MADE HER 
SECOND VAULT, FOR THE PERFORMANCES WERE STILL TO COME. WHO CAN SAY 
WHAT THE RUSSIANS WOULD HAVE SCORED WITHOUT HER AWESOME PROOF OF 
AMERICAN COMPETITIVENESS? IT HAD TO HAVE AN EFFECT ON THEM--YOU CAN 
BELIEVE IT KEPT THE PRESSURE ON THEM--SO DONT TELL ME THAT HER VAULT 
WASNT NEEDED!
	ABOVE ANYONE ELSE IN THE OLYMPICS, KERRI STRUG SHOWS WHAT IT TAKES 
TO BE A WINNER, AND HIDDEN WITHIN THE DETAILS OF HER VICTORY ARE THE 
ELEMENTS OF A TRUE BIBLICAL PARABLE. THE PARABLE ILLUSTRATES OUR 
SCRIPTURE FOR THIS MORNING, PAULS EXHORTATION TO THE CHURCH AT ROME, THE 
VERY HEART OF HIS EPISTLE TO THE ROMANS.
	ITS MUCH, MUCH MORE THAN MERELY HAVING A WINNING ATTITUDE OR THE 
POWER OF POSITIVE THINKING. THIS SCRIPTURE CASTS THE SPIRITUAL FOUNDATION 
FOR VICTORIOUS LIVING, OR, TO USE THE WORDS OF PAUL HIMSELF, WHAT IT MEANS 
TO BE EVEN MORE THAN A CONQUEROR. I SEE FIVE POWERFUL AFFIRMATIONS 
EMANATING FROM THIS LIFE-CHANGING SCRIPTURE:
	1. GOD IS FOR US. IF THAT IS TRUE, 
		THEN WHO CARES WHO MAY BE AGAINST US?
	2. IF GOD GAVE US HIS ONLY BEGOTTEN SON, 
		THEN GOD WILL SURELY ALSO GIVE US EVERYTHING ELSE WE MAY NEED.
	3. IF GOD JUSTIFIES US, THEN NO ONE CAN CONDEMN US.
	4. THE RESURRECTION OF CHRIST FROM THE DEAD IS ABSOLUTELY ESSENTIAL
		FOR HIS ABILITY TO INTERCEDE FOR US AND OUR SINS BEFORE THE RIGHT 
		HAND OF GOD. 
	5. NOTHING IN ALL CREATION CAN EVER SEPARATE US 
		FROM THE LOVE OF GOD, EVER AGAIN.
	ONLY GOD CAN GIVE US THE ADVANCE ASSURANCE OF VICTORY. THE ADVANCE 
ASSURANCE OF VICTORY IS NOT WELL-KNOWN BY THE WORLD, BUT CAN ONLY BE 
FULLY KNOWN BY THE JUSTIFIED BELIEVER IN JESUS CHRIST. IT IS GOD WHO 
JUSTIFIES... (VERSE 33) WHAT DOES IT MEAN TO BE JUSTIFIED?
	DURING HIS SERMON AT THE SATURDAY CELEBRATION OF THE HARVEST 
CRUSADE, PASTOR GREG LAURIE GAVE THE BEST DEFINITION OF JUSTIFICATION THAT 
I HAVE EVER HEARD. JUSTIFICATION IS USUALLY A RATHER DRY CONCEPT FROM 
EARLY LUTHERAN THEOLOGY. MARTIN LUTHER WANTED TO INVALIDATE THE ROMAN 
CATHOLIC NOTION THAT A WEALTHY PERSON COULD GUARANTEE A BETTER PLACE 
FOR THEMSELVES IN HEAVEN THROUGH THEIR GOOD WORKS, SYMBOLIZED BY THE 
FUND-RAISING GIMMICK OF SELLING SO-CALLED INDULGENCES OR SPECIAL PAPAL 
BLESSINGS. HE CALLED SUCH INDULGENCES ANTI-CHRIST: FOR THEY IGNORED THE 
SAVING POWER OF THE BLOOD OF JESUS, POURED OUT FOR ALL PEOPLE FOR THE 
FORGIVENESS OF SINS.
	IN ORDER TO UNDERSTAND JUSTIFICATION, GREG LAURIE TOLD US, IMAGINE 
YOURSELF ONE MILLION DOLLARS IN DEBT, SO FAR IN DEBT THAT THERE IS NO WAY 
YOU CAN EVER POSSIBLY CLEAR UP THE DEBT. HOW AWFUL--HOW TERRIBLE IT 
WOULD FEEL! YOU CONSIDER ALL OF YOUR OPTIONS: DECLARING BANKRUPTCY, 
RUNNING AWAY AND CHANGING YOUR NAME, EVEN ENDING YOUR OWN LIFE AHEAD 
OF ITS TIME. BUT JUST WHEN THE SITUATION LOOKS BLEAKEST, A FRIEND COMES TO 
YOU AND SAYS THAT YOUR DEBT HAS BEEN PAID. YOU PROTEST IN DISBELIEF: 
YOURE CRAZY; I OWE A MILLION DOLLARS! GO TO THE BANK AND CHECK YOUR 
ACCOUNT BALANCE NOW, URGES THE FRIEND. NO WAY! YOU SAY. BUT THE FRIEND 
PERSISTS, NOW JUST DO THIS THING ONE TIME FOR ME--GO AND CHECK YOUR 
ACCOUNT. AND WHEN YOU DO, YOU DISCOVER TO YOUR ABSOLUTE AMAZEMENT 
THAT YOUR FRIEND IS RIGHT. YOUR DEBT HAS BEEN WIPED AWAY! YOU NO LONGER 
OWE A MILLION DOLLARS! AND WHAT IS MORE, THERE IS A POSITIVE BALANCE IN 
YOUR ACCOUNT OF $5 MILLION! AND THAT IS JUSTIFICATION! IN MY QUARTER-
CENTURY OF MINISTRY I HAD NEVER BEFORE HEARD 60,000 CHRISTIANS CHEERING 
ABOUT JUSTIFICATION; IT LITERALLY SENT CHILLS DOWN MY SPINE.  
	NOW IMAGINE HOW MUCH DIFFERENT, HOW MUCH BETTER YOUR LIFE WOULD BE 
IF YOU COULD JUST HOLD ONTO THAT TREMENDOUS FEELING OF BEING JUSTIFIED, 
YOUR DEBIT RENDERED INTO A CREDIT, AS FAR ABOVE GROUND AS YOU USED TO BE 
IN A HOLE. THATS THE MEANING OF BEING MORE THAN A CONQUEROR. THE 
TROUBLE WITH WORLDLY CONQUERORS, YOU SEE, IS THAT TOO OFTEN THEY GET THE 
NOTION INTO THEIR HEAD THAT THEY ALONE ARE RESPONSIBLE FOR THEIR OWN 
SUCCESS. THEY FORGET TO GIVE DUE CREDIT TO A HIGHER POWER, THE POWER THAT 
PROVIDED THEM WITH ALL THE RESOURCES THAT WERE NEEDED TO WIN THE 
VICTORY IN THE FIRST PLACE. WITHOUT A SENSE OF GOD, CONQUERORS MAY 
LITERALLY WIND UP SNATCHING DEFEAT FROM THE JAWS OF VICTORY.
	THE OTHER SIDE OF THE COIN IS JUST AS IMPORTANT. TO BE JUSTIFIED DOES 
NOT MEAN THAT THERE IS NOTHING MORE WE CAN DO OR NOTHING MORE THAT WE 
NEED TO DO. ALTHOUGH CHRIST HAS SECURED THE VICTORY ALREADY, OUR 
PARTICIPATION IN HIS VICTORY IS STILL REQUIRED. THE FINAL SCORE SHOWED THAT 
KERRI STRUG MAY NOT HAVE NEEDED TO MAKE THAT SECOND VAULT, BUT SHE 
DIDNT KNOW IT AT THE TIME! ALL THAT SHE KNEW WERE FOUR THINGS: HER BOSS 
HAD CALLED FOR BETTER THAN HER BEST, THE CLOCK WAS TICKING. SHE WAS 
INJURED, AND THAT HER TEAMS HOPES AND DREAMS WERE RESTING IN HER 
SHOULDERS. SO KERRI DID THE ONE THING THAT ANY CHRISTIAN SHOULD DO WHEN 
THE CHIPS ARE DOWN AND ITS DO OR DIE: SHE PRAYED TO GOD, FROM WHENCE 
COMETH HER HELP. AND THEN SHE SOARED INTO THE HISTORY BOOKS. 
	MY PRAYER FOR YOU TODAY IS THAT YOU WOULD LEARN THE SECRET AND 
THAT YOU WOULD TASTE THE THRILL OF VICTORIOUS LIVING THROUGH JESUS CHRIST 
OUR RESURRECTED LORD. FOR NOTHING IN ALL CREATION, NEITHER LOSING NOR 
WINNING, CAN EVER SEPARATE YOU FROM HIS GREAT AND GRACIOUS LOVE. AMEN.
</PRE>
<P>
