<A NAME="Book-A"><H2>A: BOOK TITLES</H2> and reviews</A>
<A HREF="http://www.mindspring.com:80/~walter/reviews7.html#alone">Alone with the Dead, by Robert J. Randisi</A>: Review

<A NAME="Book-B"><H2>B: BOOK TITLES</H2> and reviews</A>
