<DOCOLDNO>IA064-000370-B006-347</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.magicdragon.com:80/Wallace/thomson.html 206.149.251.176 19970112064943 text/html 1809
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Sun, 12 Jan 1997 06:54:24 GMT
