<center><H2>SURFLANT Pro-Active Maintenance (SPAM)</H2></center>
<HR>
</HEAD>
<BODY TEXT="#000000" LINK="#0000FF" ALINK="#FF0000" VLINK="#8E36B">
SPAM is a Reliability-Centered Maintenance (RCM) Process of evaluating
the maintenance strategy of the selected systems.

